# <a name="sensitive-information-type-entity-definitions"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-104">Определения типов конфиденциальной информации</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-104">Sensitive information type entity definitions</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-105">Защита от потери данных (DLP) в центре соответствия требованиям включает множество типов конфиденциальной информации, готовых к использованию в политиках защиты от потери данных.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-105">Data loss prevention (DLP) in the Compliance Center includes many sensitive information types that are ready for you to use in your DLP policies.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="548bb-106">В этой статье перечислены все эти типы конфиденциальной информации и показано, каким именно образом политика защиты от потери данных выявляет каждый тип.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-106">This topic lists all of these sensitive information types and shows what a DLP policy looks for when it detects each type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="548bb-107">Тип конфиденциальной информации определяется шаблоном, который можно идентифицировать регулярным выражением или функцией.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-107">A sensitive information type is defined by a pattern that can be identified by a regular expression or a function.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="548bb-108">Кроме того, для идентификации типа конфиденциальной информации могут использоваться подкрепляющие доказательства, такие как ключевые слова и контрольные суммы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-108">In addition, corroborative evidence such as keywords and checksums can be used to identify a sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="548bb-109">Уровень вероятности и расположение слов и знаков также используются в процессе оценки.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-109">Confidence level and proximity are also used in the evaluation process.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-110">Для типов конфиденциальной информации требуется одна из следующих подписок:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-110">Sensitive information types require one of these subscriptions:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-111">Microsoft 365 E3</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-111">Microsoft 365 E3</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-112">Microsoft 365 E5</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-112">Microsoft 365 E5</span></span>

## <a name="aba-routing-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-113">Номер маршрутизации код банка ABA</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-113">ABA routing number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-114">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-114">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-115">девять цифр, которые могут быть в форматированном или неформатированном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-115">nine digits which may be in a formatted or unformatted pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-116">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-116">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-117">Форматируемые</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-117">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-118">четыре цифры, начинающиеся с 0, 1, 2, 3, 6, 7 или 8.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-118">four digits beginning with 0, 1, 2, 3, 6, 7, or 8</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-119">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-119">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-120">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-120">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-121">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-121">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-122">цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-122">a digit</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-123">Неформатированный: девять последовательных цифр, начиная с 0, 1, 2, 3, 6, 7 или 8.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-123">Unformatted: nine consecutive digits beginning with 0, 1, 2, 3, 6, 7, or 8</span></span> 

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-124">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-124">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-125">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-125">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-126">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-126">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-127">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-127">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-128">функция Func_aba_routing находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-128">The function Func_aba_routing finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-129">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_ABA_Routing.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-129">A keyword from Keyword_ABA_Routing is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-130">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-130">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-131">функция Func_aba_routing находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-131">The function Func_aba_routing finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- ABA Routing Number -->
    <Entity id="cb353f78-2b72-4c3c-8827-92ebe4f69fdf" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_aba_routing" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ABA_Routing" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_aba_routing" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="argentina-national-identity-dni-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-149">Внутренний идентификационный номер (DNI), Аргентина</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-149">Argentina national identity (DNI) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-150">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-150">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-151">Восемь цифр с периодами или без них</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-151">Eight digits with or without periods</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-152">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-152">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-153">Восемь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-153">Eight digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-154">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-154">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-155">Необязательный период</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-155">an optional period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-156">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-156">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-157">Необязательный период</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-157">an optional period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-158">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-158">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-159">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-159">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-160">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-160">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-161">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-161">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-162">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-162">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-163">регулярное выражение Regex_argentina_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-163">The regular expression Regex_argentina_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-164">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_argentina_national_id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-164">A keyword from Keyword_argentina_national_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Argentina National Identity (DNI) Number -->
<Entity id="eefbb00e-8282-433c-8620-8f1da3bffdb2" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Regex_argentina_national_id"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_argentina_national_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="australia-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-176">Номер банковского счета для Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-176">Australia bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-177">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-177">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-178">от шести до десяти цифр со номером филиала банка или без него</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-178">six to ten digits with or without a bank state branch number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-179">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-179">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-180">Номер счета — от шести до десяти цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-180">Account number is six to ten digits.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-181">Номер филиала государственного банка Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-181">Australia bank state branch number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-182">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-182">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-183">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-183">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-184">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-184">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-185">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-185">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-186">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-186">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-187">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-187">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-188">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-188">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-189">регулярное выражение Regex_australia_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-189">The regular expression Regex_australia_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern..</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-190">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_australia_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-190">A keyword from Keyword_australia_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-191">регулярное выражение Regex_australia_bank_account_number_bsb находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-191">The regular expression Regex_australia_bank_account_number_bsb finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-192">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-192">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-193">регулярное выражение Regex_australia_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-193">The regular expression Regex_australia_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern..</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-194">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_australia_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-194">A keyword from Keyword_australia_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Australia Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="74a54de9-2a30-4aa0-a8aa-3d9327fc07c7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Regex_australia_bank_account_number_bsb" />
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_bank_account_number" />
  </Pattern>
 </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-195">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-195">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_australia_bank_account_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-196">Keyword_australia_bank_account_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-196">Keyword_australia_bank_account_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-197">swift bank code</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-197">swift bank code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-198">correspondent bank</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-198">correspondent bank</span></span>

## <a name="australia-business-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-210">Бизнес-номер Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-210">Australia business number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-211">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-211">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-212">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-212">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-213">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-213">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-214">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-214">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-215">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-215">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-216">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-216">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>


### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-217">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-217">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-218">11 цифр с необязательными ограничителями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-218">11 digits with optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-219">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-219">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-220">11 цифр с необязательными ограничителями:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-220">11 digits with optional delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-221">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-221">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-222">Необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-222">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-223">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-223">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-224">Необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-224">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-225">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-225">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-226">Необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-226">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-227">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-227">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-228">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-228">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-229">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-229">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-230">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-230">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-231">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-231">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-232">Функция Func_australian_business_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-232">The function Func_australian_business_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-233">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_australian_business_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-233">A keyword from Keywords_australian_business_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-234">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-234">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-235">Функция Func_australian_business_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-235">The function Func_australian_business_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Australia Business Number -->
      <Entity id="76e83b3b-01ee-4530-aced-e667a6609f49" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_business_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_australian_business_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_business_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="australia-company-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-245">Номер компании Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-245">Australia company number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-246">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-246">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-247">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-247">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-248">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-248">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-249">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-249">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-250">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-250">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-251">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-251">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-252">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-252">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-253">девять цифр с разделителями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-253">nine digits with delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-254">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-254">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-255">девять цифр с разделителями:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-255">nine digits with delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-256">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-256">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-257">пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-257">a space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-258">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-258">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-259">пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-259">a space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-260">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-260">three digits</span></span>


### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-261">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-261">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-262">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-262">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-263">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-263">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-264">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-264">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-265">Функция Func_Australian_Company_Number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-265">The function Func_Australian_Company_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-266">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_Australian_Company_Number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-266">A keyword from Keyword_Australian_Company_Number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-267">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-267">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-268">Функция Func_Australian_Company_Number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-268">The function Func_Australian_Company_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Australia Company Number -->
      <Entity id="b1fba4f7-7b3e-4bb9-8f9a-9366df604dbb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Australian_Company_Number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Australian_Company_Number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Australian_Company_Number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_australia_company_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-270">Keyword_australia_company_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-270">Keyword_australia_company_number</span></span>

## <a name="australia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-278">Номер водительского удостоверения для Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-278">Australia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-279">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-279">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-280">девять букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-280">nine letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-281">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-281">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-282">девять букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-282">nine letters and digits:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-283">две цифры или буквы (без учета регистра).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-283">two digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-284">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-284">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-285">пять цифр или букв (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-285">five digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-286">OR</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-286">OR</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-287">один-два необязательных буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-287">one to two optional letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-288">от четырех до девяти цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-288">four to nine digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-289">OR</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-289">OR</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-290">девять цифр или букв (без учета регистра);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-290">nine digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-291">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-291">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-292">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-292">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-293">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-293">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-294">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-294">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-295">регулярное выражение Regex_australia_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-295">The regular expression Regex_australia_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-296">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-296">A keyword from Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-297">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number_exclusions не находится.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-297">No keyword from Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number_exclusions is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Australia Drivers License Number -->
<Entity id="1cbbc8f5-9216-4392-9eb5-5ac2298d1356" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number_exclusions" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-302">international driving permit</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-302">international driving permit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-303">дриверлиценце</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-303">DriverLicence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-304">дриверлиценцес</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-304">DriverLicences</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-305">Driver Lic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-305">Driver Lic</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-306">Driver Licence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-306">Driver Licence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-307">Driver Licences</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-307">Driver Licences</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-308">дриверслик</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-308">DriversLic</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-309">дриверслиценце</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-309">DriversLicence</span></span>

## <a name="australia-medical-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-397">Номер медицинской учетной записи Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-397">Australia medical account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-398">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-398">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-399">10–11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-399">10-11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-400">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-400">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-401">10–11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-401">10-11 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-402">Первая цифра находится в диапазоне 2-6</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-402">first digit is in the range 2-6</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-403">девятая цифра — это контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-403">ninth digit is a check digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-404">Десятая цифра — это цифра, связанная с вопросом</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-404">tenth digit is the issue digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-405">Одиннадцатая цифра (необязательно) — индивидуальный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-405">eleventh digit (optional) is the individual number</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-406">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-406">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-407">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-407">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-408">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-408">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-409">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-409">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-410">функция Func_australian_medical_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-410">The function Func_australian_medical_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-411">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-411">A keyword from Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-412">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-412">The checksum passes.</span></span>


```xml
  <!-- Australia Medical Account Number -->
<Entity id="104a99a0-3d3b-4542-a40d-ab0b9e1efe63" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_medical_account_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number"/>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_australia_medical_account_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-414">Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-414">Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-415">bank account details</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-415">bank account details</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-417">mortgage account</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-417">mortgage account</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-418">bank payments</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-418">bank payments</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-419">information branch</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-419">information branch</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-420">credit card loan</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-420">credit card loan</span></span>

## <a name="australia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-424">Номер паспорта для Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-424">Australia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-425">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-425">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-426">Буква, за которой следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-426">A letter followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-427">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-427">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-428">Буква (без учета регистра), за которой следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-428">A letter (not case sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-429">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-429">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-430">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-430">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-431">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-431">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-432">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-432">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-433">регулярное выражение Regex_australia_passport_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-433">The regular expression Regex_australia_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-434">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_passport или Keyword_australia_passport_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-434">A keyword from Keyword_passport or Keyword_australia_passport_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Australia Passport Number -->
<Entity id="29869db6-602d-4853-ab93-3484f905df50" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_passport_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_passport_number" />
        </Any>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>   
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-435">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-435">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_passport"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-436">Keyword_passport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-436">Keyword_passport</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-437">Passport Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-437">Passport Number</span></span>

## <a name="australia-tax-file-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-468">Номер файла налога для Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-468">Australia tax file number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-469">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-469">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-470">от восьми до девяти цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-470">eight to nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-471">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-471">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-472">от восьми до девяти цифр, как правило, представляются пробелы следующим образом:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-472">eight to nine digits typically presented with spaces as follows:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-473">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-473">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-474">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-474">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-475">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-475">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-476">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-476">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-477">две и три цифры, где последняя цифра — проверочная.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-477">two to three digits where the last digit is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-478">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-478">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-479">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-479">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-480">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-480">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-481">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-481">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-482">функция Func_australian_tax_file_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-482">The function Func_australian_tax_file_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-483">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_Australia_Tax_File_Number или Keyword_number_exclusions не найдено;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-483">No keyword from Keyword_Australia_Tax_File_Number or Keyword_number_exclusions is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-484">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-484">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
   <!-- Australia Tax File Number -->
    <Entity id="e29bc95f-ff70-4a37-aa01-04d17360a4c5" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_tax_file_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_Australia_Tax_File_Number" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="austria-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-496">Номер водительского удостоверения для Австрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-496">Austria driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-497">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-497">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-498">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-498">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-499">восемь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-499">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-500">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-500">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-501">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-501">eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-502">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-502">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-503">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-503">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-504">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-504">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-505">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-505">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-506">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-506">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-507">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` или `Keywords_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-507">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Austria Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="682f18ce-44eb-482b-8198-2bcb96a0761e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="austria-identity-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-634">Австрийская идентификационная карточка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-634">Austria identity card</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-635">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-635">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-636">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-636">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-637">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-637">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-638">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-638">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-639">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-639">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-640">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-640">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-641">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-641">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-642">24 – символическое сочетание букв, цифр и специальных символов;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-642">A 24-character combination of letters, digits, and special characters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-643">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-643">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-644">24 символа:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-644">24 characters:</span></span>
  
-  <span data-ttu-id="548bb-645">22 буквы (без учета регистра), цифры, обратные косые черты, косые черты и знаки плюса</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-645">22 letters (not case-sensitive), digits, backslashes, forward slashes, or plus signs</span></span> 
    
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-646">две буквы (без учета регистра), цифры, обратные косые черты, знаки косой черты, знаки плюса и знаки равенства.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-646">two letters (not case-sensitive), digits, backslashes, forward slashes, plus signs, or equal signs</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-647">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-647">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-648">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-648">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-649">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-649">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-650">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-650">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-651">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_austria_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-651">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-652">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-652">A keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
   
```xml
      <!-- Austria Identity Card -->
      <Entity id="5ec06c3b-007e-4820-8343-7ff73b889735" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="austria-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-658">Номер паспорта для Австрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-658">Austria passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-659">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе сенситивеинформатион Passport Number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-659">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitiveinformation type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-660">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-660">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-661">Одна буква, за которой следует необязательный пробел и семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-661">One letter followed by an optional space and seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-662">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-662">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-663">Сочетание одной буквы, семи цифр и одного пробела:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-663">A combination of one letter, seven digits, and one space:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-664">одна буква (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-664">one letter (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-665">один пробел (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-665">one space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-666">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-666">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-667">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-667">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-668">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-668">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-669">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-669">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-670">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-670">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-671">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_austria_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-671">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-672">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-672">A keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-675">службу #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-675">passport#</span></span>

## <a name="austria-social-security-number-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-693">Австрийский номер социального страхования или эквивалентная идентификация</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-693">Austria social security number or equivalent identification</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-694">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в номере социального страхования ЕС или эквивалентного идентификатора.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-694">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Social Security Number or Equivalent ID sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-695">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-695">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-696">10 цифр в указанном формате</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-696">10 digits in the specified format</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-697">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-697">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-698">10 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-698">10 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-699">три цифры, соответствующие серийному номеру.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-699">three digits that correspond to a serial number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-700">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-700">one check digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-701">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (ДДММГГ —)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-701">six digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMYY)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-702">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-702">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-703">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-703">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-704">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-704">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-705">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-705">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-706">Функция "Func_austria_eu_</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-706">The function  \`Func_austria_eu_</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-707">_or_equivalent ' находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-707">_or_equivalent\` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-708">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-708">a keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-709">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-709">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-710">Функция  `Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-710">The function  `Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU SSN or Equivalent Number -->
<Entity id="d24e32a4-c0bb-4ba8-899d-6303b95742d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
            <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="austria-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-726">Налоговый идентификационный номер для Австрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-726">Austria tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-727">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-727">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-728">девять цифр с необязательным дефисом и косой чертой.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-728">nine digits with optional hyphen and forward slash</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-729">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-729">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-730">девять цифр с необязательным дефисом и косой чертой.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-730">nine digits with optional hyphen and forward slash:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-731">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-731">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-732">дефис (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-732">a hyphen (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-733">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-733">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-734">косая черта (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-734">a forward slash (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-735">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-735">four digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-736">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-736">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-737">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-737">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-738">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-738">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-739">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-739">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-740">Функция  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-740">The function  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-741">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-741">A keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-742">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-742">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-743">Функция  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-743">The function  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Austria Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="4fd58d22-af28-4451-b18a-6f722430a56d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="austria-value-added-tax"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-766">Налог на добавленную стоимость (Австрия)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-766">Austria value added tax</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-767">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-767">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-768">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-768">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-769">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-769">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-770">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-770">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-771">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-771">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-772">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-772">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-773">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-773">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-774">11-буквенно-буквенно-буквенный шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-774">11-character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-775">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-775">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-776">11-буквенно-цифровой буквенно-значный шаблон:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-776">11-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-777">A или a</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-777">A or a</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-778">T или t</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-778">T or t</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-779">Необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-779">Optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-780">U или u</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-780">U or u</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-781">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-781">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-782">две или три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-782">two or three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-783">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-783">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-784">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-784">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-785">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-785">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-786">одна или две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-786">one or two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-787">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-787">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-788">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-788">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-789">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-789">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-790">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-790">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-791">Функция Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-791">The function Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

## <a name="azure-documentdb-auth-key"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-812">Ключ проверки подлинности Azure DocumentDB</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-812">Azure DocumentDB auth key</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-813">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-813">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-814">Строка "DocumentDb", за которой следуют символы и строки, описанные в приведенном ниже шаблоне.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-814">The string "DocumentDb" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-815">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-815">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-816">Строка "DocumentDb"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-816">The string "DocumentDb"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-817">Любая комбинация из 3-200 прописных или строчных букв, цифр, символов, специальных символов и пробелов.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-817">Any combination of between 3-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-818">Символ "больше" (>), знак равенства (=), кавычки (") или апостроф (')</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-818">A greater than symbol (>), an equal sign (=), a quotation mark ("), or an apostrophe (')</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-819">Любая комбинация 86 строчных или прописных букв, цифр, символов косой черты (/) или знака плюса (+).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-819">Any combination of 86 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-820">Два знака равенства (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-820">Two equal signs (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-821">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-821">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-822">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-822">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-823">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-823">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-824">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-824">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-825">Регулярное выражение CEP_Regex_AzureDocumentDBAuthKey находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-825">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureDocumentDBAuthKey finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-826">Регулярное выражение CEP_CommonExampleKeywords не **находит содержимое** , которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-826">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords does **not** find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Azure Document DB Auth Key -->
<Entity id="0f587d92-eb28-44a9-bd1c-90f2892b47aa" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureDocumentDBAuthKey" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
          </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

Azure.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-853">The string "cloudapp.azure.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="548bb-854">com "," клаудапп. - <span data-ttu-id="548bb-861">ноль — два символа пробела</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-861">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-905">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-905">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-906">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-906">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-907">Регулярное выражение CEP_Regex_AzureIoTConnectionString находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-907">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureIoTConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-908">Регулярное выражение CEP_CommonExampleKeywords не **находит содержимое** , которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-908">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords does **not** find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure IoT Connection String-->
<Entity id="0b34bec3-d5d6-4974-b7b0-dcdb5c90c29d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureIoTConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-924">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-924">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-925">Строка "усерпвд =", за которой следует буквенно-цифровая строка.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-925">The string "userpwd=" followed by an alphanumeric string.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-928">Любая комбинация букв или цифр в нижнем регистре 60</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-928">any combination of 60 lowercase letters or digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-929">знак кавычек (")</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-929">a quotation mark (")</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-932">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-932">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-933">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-933">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-934">Регулярное выражение CEP_Regex_AzurePublishSettingPasswords находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-934">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzurePublishSettingPasswords finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-935">Регулярное выражение CEP_CommonExampleKeywords не **находит содержимое** , которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-935">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords does **not** find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>


```xml
<!--Azure Publish Setting Password-->
<Entity id="75f4cc8a-a68e-49e5-89ce-fa8f03d286a5" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
       <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzurePublishSettingPasswords" />
       <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
           <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
       </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

Windows.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-952">The string "redis.cache.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="548bb-953">NET, за которыми следуют символы и строки, описанные в приведенном ниже шаблоне, в том числе строку "Password" или "pwd".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-953">net" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the string "password" or "pwd".</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-955">строка "Redis. Cache. Windows.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-955">the string "redis.cache.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="548bb-956">команде</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-956">net"</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-967">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-967">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

## <a name="azure-sas"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-984">SAS Azure</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-984">Azure SAS</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-985">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-985">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-986">Строка "SIG", за которой следуют символы и строки, описанные в приведенном ниже шаблоне.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-986">The string "sig" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-987">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-987">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-988">строка "SIG"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-988">the string "sig"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-989">ноль — два символа пробела</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-989">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-990">знак равенства (=);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-990">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-991">ноль — два символа пробела</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-991">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-992">любое сочетание 43-53 символов, которые являются буквами нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифрами или знаком процента (%)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-992">any combination of between 43-53 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, or the percent sign (%)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-993">строка "% 3D"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-993">the string "%3d"</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-998">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-998">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

```xml
</Entity>
```

## <a name="azure-service-bus-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-1000">Строка подключения к служебной шине Azure</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-1000">Azure service bus connection string</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-1001">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-1001">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-1002">Строка "EndPoint", за которой следуют символы и строки, описанные в приведенном ниже шаблоне, в том числе строки "сервицебус. Windows.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-1002">The string "EndPoint" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the strings "servicebus.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="548bb-1003">NET "и" Шаредакцескэй ".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-1003">net" and "SharedAccesKey".</span></span>
