## <a name="france-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-4888">Значение налогового номера, добавленного в Франции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4888">France value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-4889">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4889">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-4890">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4890">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-4891">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4891">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-4892">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4892">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-4893">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4893">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-4894">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4894">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-4895">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4895">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-4896">13-буквенно-буквенно-цифровой шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4896">13 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-4897">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4897">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-4898">13 символов буквенно-цифрового шаблона:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4898">13 character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-4899">две буквы — FR (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4899">two letters  - FR (case insensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-4900">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4900">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-4901">две буквы или цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4901">two letters or digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-4902">необязательный пробел, точка, дефис или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4902">an optional space, dot, hyphen or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-4903">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4903">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-4904">необязательный пробел, точка, дефис или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4904">an optional space, dot, hyphen or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-4905">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4905">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-4906">необязательный пробел, точка, дефис или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4906">an optional space, dot, hyphen or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-4907">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4907">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-4908">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4908">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-4909">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4909">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-4910">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4910">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-4911">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4911">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-4912">Функция Func_france_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4912">The function Func_france_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-4913">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_france_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4913">A keyword from Keywords_france_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-4914">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4914">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-4915">Функция Func_france_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4915">The function Func_france_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- France Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="949121e6-ad9f-4379-8731-710342baea78" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_france_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-4916">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4916">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_france_value_added_tax_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-4917">Keyword_France_value_added_tax_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4917">Keyword_France_value_added_tax_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-4918">номер НДС</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4918">vat number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-4920">процент #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4920">vat#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-4921">налог на добавленную стоимость</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4921">value added tax</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-4922">Siren идентификация No нумéро д'идентификатион таксе Сур валеур ажаутéе</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4922">siren identification no numéro d'identification taxe sur valeur ajoutée</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-4923">таксе валеур ажаутéе</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4923">taxe valeur ajoutée</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-4924">таксе Сур Ла валеур ажаутéе</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4924">taxe sur la valeur ajoutée</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-4925">n ° тва</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4925">n° tva</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-4926">нумéро de тва</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4926">numéro de tva</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-4927">нумéро д'идентификатион Siren</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4927">numéro d'identification siren</span></span>


## <a name="germany-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-4928">Номер водительского удостоверения для Германии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4928">Germany driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-4929">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включен в тип конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4929">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-4930">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4930">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-4931">сочетание 11 цифр и букв</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4931">combination of 11 digits and letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-4932">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4932">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-4933">11 цифр и букв (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4933">11 digits and letters (not case sensitive):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-4934">цифра или буква;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4934">a digit or letter</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-4935">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4935">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-4936">шесть цифр или букв</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4936">six digits or letters</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-4937">цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4937">a digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-4938">цифра или буква;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4938">a digit or letter</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-4939">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4939">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-4940">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4940">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-4941">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4941">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-4942">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4942">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-4943">Функция Func_german_drivers_license находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4943">The function Func_german_drivers_license finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-4944">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_german_drivers_license_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4944">A keyword from Keyword_german_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-4945">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4945">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- German Driver's License Number -->
    <Entity id="91da9335-1edb-45b7-a95f-5fe41a16c63c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_german_drivers_license" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_german_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-4946">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4946">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_german_drivers_license_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-4947">Keyword_german_drivers_license_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4947">Keyword_german_drivers_license_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-4948">аусстеллунгсдатум</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4948">ausstellungsdatum</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-4949">аусстеллунгсорт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4949">ausstellungsort</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-4950">ausstellende behöde</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4950">ausstellende behöde</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-4951">ausstellende behorde</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4951">ausstellende behorde</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-4952">ausstellende behoerde</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-4952">ausstellende behoerde</span></span>

## <a name="germany-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5094">Номер идентификационной карточки для Германии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5094">Germany identity card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5095">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5095">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5096">с 1 ноября 2010: девять букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5096">since 1 November 2010: Nine letters and digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5097">от 1 апреля 1987 до 31 октября 2010:10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5097">from 1 April 1987 until 31 October 2010: 10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5098">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5098">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5099">с 1 ноября 2010:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5099">since 1 November 2010:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5100">одна буква (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5100">one letter (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5101">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5101">eight digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5102">от 1 апреля 1987 до 31 октября 2010:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5102">from 1 April 1987 until 31 October 2010:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5103">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5103">ten digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5104">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5104">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5105">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5105">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5106">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5106">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5107">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5107">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5108">регулярное выражение Regex_germany_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5108">The regular expression Regex_germany_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5109">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_germany_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5109">A keyword from Keyword_germany_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Germany Identity Card Number -->
<Entity id="e577372f-c42e-47a0-9d85-bebed1c237d4" recommendedConfidence="65" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_germany_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_germany_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5110">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5110">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_germany_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5111">Keyword_germany_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5111">Keyword_germany_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5112">аусвеис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5112">ausweis</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5113">гпид</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5113">gpid</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5114">процедура</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5114">identification</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5115">идентификатион</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5115">identifikation</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5116">идентифизиерунгснуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5116">identifizierungsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5117">identity card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5117">identity card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5118">идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5118">identity number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5119">ID — нуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5119">id-nummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5120">личный идентификатор</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5120">personal id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5121">персоналаусвеис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5121">personalausweis</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5122">Идентификатор персöнличе нуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5122">persönliche id nummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5123">персöнличе идентификатионснуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5123">persönliche identifikationsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5124">персöнличе — ID — нуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5124">persönliche-id-nummer</span></span>


## <a name="germany-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5125">Номер паспорта для Германии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5125">Germany passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5126">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включен в тип конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5126">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5127">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5127">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5128">десять цифр или букв</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5128">ten digits or letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5129">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5129">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5130">Шаблон должен включать в себя все указанные ниже элементы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5130">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5131">Первый символ — цифра или буква из этого набора (C, F, G, H, J, K)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5131">first character is a digit or a letter from this set (C, F, G, H, J, K)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5132">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5132">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5133">пять цифр или букв из этого набора (C,-H, J-N, P, R, T, V-Z)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5133">five digits or letters from this set (C, -H, J-N, P, R, T, V-Z)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5134">цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5134">a digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5135">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5135">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5136">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5136">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5137">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5137">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5138">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5138">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5139">функция Func_german_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5139">The function Func_german_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5140">Найдено ключевое слово FROM `Keyword_german_passport` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5140">A keyword from `Keyword_german_passport` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5141">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5141">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5142">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5142">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5143">функция Func_german_passport_data находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5143">The function Func_german_passport_data finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5144">Найдено ключевое слово FROM `Keyword_german_passport` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5144">A keyword from `Keyword_german_passport` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5145">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5145">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- German Passport Number -->
    <Entity id="2e3da144-d42b-47ed-b123-fbf78604e52c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_german_passport" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_german_passport_data" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="germany-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5157">Идентификационный номер налогоплательщика (Германия)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5157">Germany tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5158">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5158">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5159">11 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5159">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5160">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5160">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5161">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5161">11 digits :</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5162">Две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5162">Two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5163">Необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5163">An optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5164">Три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5164">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5165">Необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5165">An optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5166">Три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5166">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5167">Необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5167">An optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5168">Две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5168">Two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5169">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5169">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5170">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5170">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5171">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5171">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5172">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5172">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5173">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5173">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5174">Функция  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5174">The function  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5175">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5175">A keyword from  `Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5176">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5176">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5177">Функция  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5177">The function  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Germany Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="43316a89-9880-40cf-b980-04bc7eefcec5" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5178">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5178">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5179">Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5179">Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5180">идентификатионснуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5180">identifikationsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5181">Идентификатор стеуер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5181">steuer id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5182">стеуеридентификатионснуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5182">steueridentifikationsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5183">стеуернуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5183">steuernummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5184">tax id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5184">tax id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5185">Налоговый идентификатор</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5185">tax identification no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5186">идентификационный номер налога</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5186">tax identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5187">налог без #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5187">tax no#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5188">налог без</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5188">tax no</span></span>

## <a name="germany-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5203">Значение налогового номера добавленного в Германии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5203">Germany value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5204">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5204">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5205">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5205">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5206">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5206">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5207">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5207">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5208">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5208">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5209">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5209">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5210">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5210">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5211">11 буквенно-цифрового шаблона</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5211">11 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5212">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5212">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5213">11-буквенно-цифровой буквенно-значный шаблон:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5213">11-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5214">буква D или d</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5214">a letter D or d</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5215">буква E или e</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5215">a letter E or e</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5216">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5216">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5217">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5217">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5218">необязательный пробел или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5218">an optional space or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5219">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5219">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5220">необязательный пробел или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5220">an optional space or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5221">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5221">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5222">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5222">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5223">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5223">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5224">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5224">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5225">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5225">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5226">Функция Func_germany_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5226">The function Func_germany_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5227">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_germany_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5227">A keyword from Keywords_germany_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5228">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5228">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5229">Функция Func_germany_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5229">The function Func_germany_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Germany Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="db177eb2-8811-4842-bffc-128c14aa219f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_germany_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5235">НДС # мехрвертстеуер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5235">vat#  mehrwertsteuer</span></span>

## <a name="greece-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5239">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера Греция</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5239">Greece driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5240">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включен в тип конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5240">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5241">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5241">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5242">девять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5242">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5243">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5243">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5244">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5244">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5245">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5245">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5246">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5246">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5247">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5247">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5248">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5248">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5249">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5249">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5250">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` или `Keywords_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5250">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Greece Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="7a2200b5-aacf-4e3c-ab36-136d3e68b7da" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="greece-national-id-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5376">Национальный идентификационный номер карты (Греция)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5376">Greece national ID card</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5377">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5377">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5378">Сочетание 7–8 букв и чисел, а также тире.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5378">Combination of 7-8 letters and numbers plus a dash</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5379">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5379">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5380">Семь букв и чисел (старый формат):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5380">Seven letters and numbers (old format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5381">одна буква (любая буква греческого алфавита);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5381">One letter (any letter of the Greek alphabet)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5382">тире;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5382">A dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5383">шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5383">Six digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5384">Восемь букв и чисел (новый формат):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5384">Eight letters and numbers (new format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5385">две буквы, которые в прописном виде есть как в греческом, так и латинском алфавите (ABEZHIKMNOPTYX);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5385">Two letters whose uppercase character occurs in both the Greek and Latin alphabets (ABEZHIKMNOPTYX)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5386">тире;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5386">A dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5387">шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5387">Six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5388">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5388">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5389">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5389">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5390">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5390">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5391">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5391">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5392">регулярное выражение Regex_greece_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5392">The regular expression Regex_greece_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5393">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_greece_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5393">A keyword from Keyword_greece_id_card is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5394">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5394">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5395">регулярное выражение Regex_greece_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5395">The regular expression Regex_greece_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Greece National ID Card -->
      <Entity id="82568215-1da1-46d3-874a-d2294d81b5ac" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_greece_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5398">Греческий идентификатор</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5398">greek id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5400">Греческая личная идентификационная карточка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5400">greek personal id card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5401">код греческой политики</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5401">greek police id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5402">identity card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5402">identity card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5403">таутотита</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5403">tautotita</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5404">ταυτότητα</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5404">ταυτότητα</span></span>

## <a name="greece-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5406">Номер паспорта для Греция</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5406">Greece passport number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5407">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5407">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5408">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5408">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5409">Две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5409">Two letters followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5410">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5410">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5411">Две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5411">Two letters followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5412">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5412">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5413">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5413">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5414">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5414">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5415">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5415">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5416">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_greece_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5416">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5417">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` или `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5417">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` or `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="greece-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5434">Идентификационный номер налога в Греция</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5434">Greece tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5435">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5435">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5436">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5436">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5437">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5437">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5438">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5438">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5439">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5439">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5440">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5440">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5441">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5441">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5442">Девять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5442">Nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5443">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5443">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5444">Девять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5444">Nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5445">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5445">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5446">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5446">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5447">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5447">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5448">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5448">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5449">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_greece_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5449">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5450">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_greece_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5450">A keyword from  `Keywords_greece_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Greek Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="15a54a5a-53d4-4080-ad43-a2a4fe1d3bf7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="hong-kong-identity-card-hkid-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5479">Номер идентификационной карточки Гонконг (HKID)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5479">Hong Kong identity card (HKID) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5480">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5480">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5481">Сочетание 8–9 букв и чисел, а также необязательные скобки вокруг последнего символа.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5481">Combination of 8-9 letters and numbers plus optional parentheses around the final character</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5482">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5482">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5483">Сочетание 8–9 букв:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5483">Combination of 8-9 letters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5484">1–2 буквы (без учета регистра);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5484">1-2 letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5485">шесть цифр; </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5485">Six digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5486">последний символ (любая цифра или буква "A") является проверочной цифрой и заключен в скобки (необязательно).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5486">The final character (any digit or the letter A), which is the check digit and is optionally enclosed in parentheses.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5487">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5487">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5488">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5488">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5489">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5489">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5490">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5490">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5491">функция Func_hong_kong_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5491">The function Func_hong_kong_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5492">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_hong_kong_id_card;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5492">A keyword from Keyword_hong_kong_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5493">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5493">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5494">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5494">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5495">функция Func_hong_kong_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5495">The function Func_hong_kong_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5496">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5496">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Hong Kong Identity Card (HKID) number -->
<Entity id="e63c28a7-ad29-4c17-a41a-3d2a0b70fd9c" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_hong_kong_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_hong_kong_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_hong_kong_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="hungary-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5536">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера Венгрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5536">Hungary driver's license number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5537">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5537">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5538">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5538">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5539">Две буквы, за которыми следуют шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5539">Two letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5540">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5540">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5541">Две буквы и шесть цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5541">Two letters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5542">Две буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5542">Two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5543">шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5543">Six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5544">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5544">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5545">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5545">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5546">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5546">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5547">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5547">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5548">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5548">The regular expression  `Regex_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5549">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` или `Keywords_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5549">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <Entity id="9d31c46b-6e6b-444c-aeb1-6dd7e604bb24" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="hungary-personal-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5674">Венгрия персональный идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5674">Hungary personal identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5675">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5675">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5676">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5676">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5677">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5677">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5678">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5678">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5679">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5679">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5680">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5680">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5681">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5681">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5682">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5682">11 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5683">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5683">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5684">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5684">11 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5685">Одна цифра, соответствующая пол (1-м-штекер, 2-гнездо, другие номера также могут иметь гражданские телефоны перед 1900 или гражданами с удвоенной гражданией)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5685">One digit that corresponds to gender (1-male, 2-female, other numbers are also possible for citizens born before 1900 or citizens with double citizenship)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5686">Шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (ГГММДД)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5686">Six digits that correspond to birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5687">Три цифры, соответствующие серийному номеру.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5687">Three digits that correspond to a serial number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5688">Одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5688">One check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5689">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5689">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5690">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5690">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5691">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5691">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5692">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5692">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5693">Функция  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5693">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5694">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5694">A keyword from  `Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5695">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5695">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5696">Функция  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5696">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Hungary Personal Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="7b5cc218-7046-47d9-80c9-f325b50896ca" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="hungary-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5707">Номер паспорта для Венгрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5707">Hungary passport number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5708">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5708">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5709">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5709">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5710">Две буквы, за которыми следуют шесть или семь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5710">Two letters followed by six or seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5711">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5711">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5712">Две буквы, за которыми следуют шесть или семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5712">Two letters followed by six or seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5713">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5713">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5714">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5714">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5715">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5715">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5716">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5716">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5717">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5717">The regular expression  `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5718">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` или `Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5718">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` or `Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="hungary-social-security-number-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5735">Венгерский номер социального страхования или идентификация эквивалентных прав</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5735">Hungary social security number or equivalent identification</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5736">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в номере социального страхования ЕС или эквивалентного идентификатора.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5736">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Social Security Number or Equivalent ID sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5737">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5737">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5738">Девять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5738">Nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5739">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5739">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5740">Девять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5740">Nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5741">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5741">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5742">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5742">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5743">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5743">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5744">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5744">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5745">Функция  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5745">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5746">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5746">A keyword from  `Keywords_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5747">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5747">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5748">Функция  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5748">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU SSN or Equivalent Number -->
<Entity id="d24e32a4-c0bb-4ba8-899d-6303b95742d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">

          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />

        </Pattern> 
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>      
</Entity>
```

## <a name="hungary-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5768">Идентификационный номер венгерского налога</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5768">Hungary tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5769">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5769">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5770">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5770">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5771">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5771">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5772">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5772">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5773">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5773">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5774">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5774">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5775">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5775">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5776">Десять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5776">Ten digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5777">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5777">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5778">Десять цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5778">Ten digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5779">Одна цифра, которая должна быть "8"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5779">One digit that must be "8"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5780">восемь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5780">Eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5781">Одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5781">One check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5782">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5782">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5783">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5783">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-5784">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5784">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5785">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5785">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5786">Функция  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5786">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5787">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5787">A keyword from  `Keywords_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-5788">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5788">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-5789">Функция  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-5789">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Hungary Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="ede42eb4-59d9-49eb-9603-d7853fbda91d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
