## <a name="japan-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6447">Номер банковского счета для Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6447">Japan bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6448">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6448">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6449">семь или восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6449">seven or eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6450">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6450">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6451">номер банковского счета:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6451">bank account number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6452">семь или восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6452">seven or eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6453">код филиала банковского счета:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6453">bank account branch code:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6454">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6454">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6455">пробел или тире (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6455">a space or dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6456">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6456">three digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6457">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6457">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6458">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6458">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6459">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6459">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6460">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6460">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6461">Функция Func_jp_bank_account находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6461">The function Func_jp_bank_account finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6462">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_bank_account.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6462">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_account is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6463">Верно одно из условий ниже:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6463">One of the following is true:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6464">функция Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6464">The function Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6465">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6465">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6466">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6466">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6467">функция Func_jp_bank_account находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6467">The function Func_jp_bank_account finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6468">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_bank_account.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6468">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_account is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="d354f95b-96ee-4b80-80bc-4377312b55bc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Version minEngineVersion="15.01.0131.000">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_bank_account" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_account" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code" />
          </Any>
      </Pattern>
  </Version>    
     <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_bank_account" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_account" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6469">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6469">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_jp_bank_account"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6470">Keyword_jp_bank_account</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6470">Keyword_jp_bank_account</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6471">Checking Account Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6471">Checking Account Number</span></span>

## <a name="japan-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6515">Номер водительского удостоверения для Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6515">Japan driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6516">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6516">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6517">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6517">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6518">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6518">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6519">12 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6519">12 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6520">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6520">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6521">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6521">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6522">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6522">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6523">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6523">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6524">функция Func_jp_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6524">The function Func_jp_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6525">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6525">A keyword from Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="c6011143-d087-451c-8313-7f6d4aed2270" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef ="Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="japan-my-number---corporate"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6563">Мой номер для Японии — корпоративный</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6563">Japan My Number - Corporate</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6564">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6564">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6565">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6565">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6566">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6566">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6567">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6567">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6568">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6568">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6569">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6569">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6570">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6570">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6571">13 цифра, цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6571">13 digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6572">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6572">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6573">13 цифра:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6573">13 digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6574">одна цифра от 1 до девяти</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6574">one digit from one to nine</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6575">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6575">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6576">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6576">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6577">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6577">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6578">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6578">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6579">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6579">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6580">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_corporate находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6580">The function Func_japanese_my_number_corporate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6581">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6581">A keyword from Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6582">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6582">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6583">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_corporate находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6583">The function Func_japanese_my_number_corporate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Japanese My Number – Corporate -->
      <Entity id="9e0eaf79-ff20-4ffb-b3e4-e7368d5db6ff" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6584">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6584">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_japan_my_number_corporate"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6585">Keyword_japan_my_number_corporate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6585">Keyword_japan_my_number_corporate</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6586">корпоративный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6586">corporate number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6587">マイナンバー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6587">マイナンバー</span></span>

## <a name="japan-my-number---personal"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6596">Япония мой номер — личное</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6596">Japan My Number - Personal</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6597">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6597">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6598">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6598">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6599">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6599">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6600">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6600">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6601">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6601">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6602">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6602">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6603">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6603">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6604">12 цифр номера</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6604">12 digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6605">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6605">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6606">12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6606">12 digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6607">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6607">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6608">необязательный пробел, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6608">an optional space, dot or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6609">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6609">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6610">необязательный пробел, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6610">an optional space, dot or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6611">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6611">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6612">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6612">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6613">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6613">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6614">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6614">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6615">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6615">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6616">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_personal находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6616">The function Func_japanese_my_number_personal finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6617">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6617">A keyword from Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6618">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6618">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6619">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_personal находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6619">The function Func_japanese_my_number_personal finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Japanese My Number – Personal -->
      <Entity id="98da8e66-7299-4ebd-9f82-c871ab37d3ef" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_personal" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_personal" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6624">個人番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6624">個人番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6625">共通番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6625">共通番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6626">マイナンバーカード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6626">マイナンバーカード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6627">マイナンバーカード番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6627">マイナンバーカード番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6628">個人番号カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6628">個人番号カード</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6630">個人識別ナンバー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6630">個人識別ナンバー</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6631">通知カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6631">通知カード</span></span>

   
## <a name="japan-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6632">Номер паспорта для Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6632">Japan passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6633">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6633">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6634">две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6634">two letters followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6635">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6635">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6636">две буквы (без учета регистра), за которыми следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6636">two letters (not case sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6637">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6637">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6638">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6638">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6639">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6639">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6640">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6640">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6641">функция Func_jp_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6641">The function Func_jp_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6642">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6642">A keyword from Keyword_jp_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Passport Number -->
<Entity id="75177310-1a09-4613-bf6d-833aae3743f8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_passport" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_passport" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="japan-residence-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6659">Номер карточки для Японии (Япония)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6659">Japan residence card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6660">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6660">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6661">12 букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6661">12 letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6662">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6662">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6663">12 букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6663">12 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6664">две буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6664">two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6665">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6665">eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6666">две буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6666">two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6667">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6667">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6668">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6668">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6669">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6669">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6670">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6670">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6671">Регулярное выражение Regex_jp_residence_card_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6671">The regular expression Regex_jp_residence_card_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6672">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_residence_card_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6672">A keyword from Keyword_jp_residence_card_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Japan Residence Card Number-->
-<Entity id="ac36fef2-a289-4e2c-bb48-b02366e89fc0" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Regex_jp_residence_card_number"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_residence_card_number"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6673">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6673">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_jp_residence_card_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6674">Keyword_jp_residence_card_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6674">Keyword_jp_residence_card_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6675">Номер карточки проживания</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6675">Residence card number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6676">Номер карточки проживания</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6676">Residence card no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6677">Карточка проживания #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6677">Residence card #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6678">在留カード番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6678">在留カード番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6679">在留カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6679">在留カード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6680">在留番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6680">在留番号</span></span>

## <a name="japan-resident-registration-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6681">Номер резидентного регистрационного номера для Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6681">Japan resident registration number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6682">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6682">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6683">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6683">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6684">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6684">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6685">11 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6685">11 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6686">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6686">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6687">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6687">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6688">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6688">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6689">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6689">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6690">функция Func_jp_resident_registration_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6690">The function Func_jp_resident_registration_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6691">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6691">A keyword from Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Resident Registration Number -->
<Entity id="01c1209b-6389-4faf-a5f8-3f7e13899652" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_resident_registration_number" />
        <Match idRef ="Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6692">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6692">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_jp_resident_registration_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6693">Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6693">Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number</span></span>

## <a name="japan-social-insurance-number-sin"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6704">Номер социального страхования для Японии (SIN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6704">Japan social insurance number (SIN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6705">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6705">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6706">7–12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6706">7-12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6707">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6707">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6708">7–12 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6708">7-12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6709">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6709">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6710">дефис (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6710">a hyphen (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6711">шесть цифр или</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6711">six digits OR</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6712">7–12 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6712">7-12 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6713">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6713">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6714">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6714">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6715">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6715">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6716">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6716">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6717">функция Func_jp_sin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6717">The function Func_jp_sin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6718">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_sin.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6718">A keyword from Keyword_jp_sin is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6719">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6719">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6720">функция Func_jp_sin_pre_1997 находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6720">The function Func_jp_sin_pre_1997 finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6721">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_sin.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6721">A keyword from Keyword_jp_sin is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Social Insurance Number -->
<Entity id="c840e719-0896-45bb-84fd-1ed5c95e45ff" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_sin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_sin" />
    </Pattern>
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_sin_pre_1997" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_sin" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="latvia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6742">Номер водительского удостоверения для Латвии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6742">Latvia driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6743">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6743">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6744">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6744">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6745">три буквы, за которыми следуют шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6745">three letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6746">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6746">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6747">три буквы и шесть цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6747">three letters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6748">три буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6748">three letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6749">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6749">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6750">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6750">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6751">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6751">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6752">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6752">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6753">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6753">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6754">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6754">The regular expression  `Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6755">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` или `Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6755">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Latvia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="ec996de0-30f2-46b1-b192-4d2ff8805fa7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="latvia-personal-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6880">Личный код Латвии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6880">Latvia personal code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6881">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6881">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6882">11 цифр и необязательный дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6882">11 digits and an optional hyphen</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6883">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6883">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6884">Старый формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6884">Old format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6885">11 цифр и дефис:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6885">11 digits and a hyphen:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6886">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (ДДММГГ —)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6886">six digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMYY)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6887">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6887">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6888">одна цифра, соответствующая столетию рождения ("0" для 19 века, "1" для 20-й век) и "2" для 21 века)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6888">one digit that corresponds to the century of birth ("0" for 19th century, "1" for 20th century, and "2" for 21st century)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6889">четыре цифры, созданные случайным образом</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6889">four digits, randomly generated</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6890">Новый формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6890">New format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6891">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6891">11 digits</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6892">Две цифры "32"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6892">Two digits "32"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6893">девять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6893">Nine digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6894">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6894">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6895">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6895">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6896">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6896">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6897">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6897">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6898">Функция  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` или регулярное выражение `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` выполняет поиск содержимого, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6898">The function  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` or the regex `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6899">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6899">A keyword from  `Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6900">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6900">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6901">Функция  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` или регулярное выражение `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` выполняет поиск содержимого, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6901">The function  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` or the regex `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Latvia Personal Code -->
      <Entity id="03fcf763-27c2-49ed-9422-2641c6c895c9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

## <a name="latvia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6964">Номер паспорта для Латвии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6964">Latvia passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6965">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6965">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6966">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6966">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6967">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6967">two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6968">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6968">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6969">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6969">two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6970">две цифры или буквы (без учета регистра).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6970">two digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6971">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6971">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6972">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6972">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6973">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6973">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6974">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6974">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6975">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6975">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6976">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6976">The regular expression  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-6977">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` или `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6977">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` or `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="lithuania-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6997">Литва номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6997">Lithuania driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-6998">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6998">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-6999">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-6999">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7000">восемь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7000">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7001">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7001">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7002">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7002">eight digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7003">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7003">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7004">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7004">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7005">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7005">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7006">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7006">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7007">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7007">The regular expression  `Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7008">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` или `Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7008">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Lithuania Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="86f7628b-e0f4-4dc3-9fbc-e4300e4c7d78" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="lithuania-personal-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7133">Литва персональный код</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7133">Lithuania personal code</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7134">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7134">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7135">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7135">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7136">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7136">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7137">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7137">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7138">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7138">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7139">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7139">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7140">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7140">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7141">11 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7141">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7142">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7142">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7143">11 цифр без пробелов и разделителей:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7143">11 digits without spaces and delimiters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7144">одна цифра (1-6), соответствующая пол и век рождения человека</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7144">one digit (1-6) that corresponds to the person's gender and century of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7145">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (ГГММДД)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7145">six digits that correspond to birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7146">три цифры, которые соответствуют серийному числу даты рождения.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7146">three digits that correspond to the serial number of the date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7147">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7147">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7148">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7148">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7149">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7149">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7150">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7150">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7151">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7151">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7152">Функция  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7152">The function  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7153">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7153">A keyword from  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7154">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7154">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7155">Функция  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7155">The function  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Lithuania Personal Code -->
      <Entity id="cd6d3786-8ec3-4524-a2cf-1e0095379171" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="lithuania-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7190">Литва номер паспорта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7190">Lithuania passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7191">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7191">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7192">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7192">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7193">восемь цифр или букв без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7193">eight digits or letters with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7194">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7194">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7195">восемь цифр или букв (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7195">eight digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7196">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7196">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7197">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7197">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7198">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7198">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7199">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7199">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7200">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7200">The regular expression  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7201">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` или `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7201">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` or `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="luxemburg-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7218">Номер водительского удостоверения Луксембург</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7218">Luxemburg driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7219">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7219">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7220">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7220">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7221">шесть цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7221">six digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7222">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7222">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7223">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7223">six digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7224">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7224">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7225">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7225">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7226">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7226">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7227">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7227">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7228">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7228">The regular expression  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7229">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` или `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7229">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="89daf717-1544-4860-9a2e-fc9166dd8852" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="luxemburg-national-identification-number-natural-persons"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7353">Национальный идентификационный номер Луксембург (для природных людей)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7353">Luxemburg national identification number (natural persons)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7354">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7354">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7355">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7355">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7356">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7356">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7357">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7357">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7358">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7358">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7359">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7359">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7360">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7360">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7361">13 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7361">13 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7362">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7362">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7363">13 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7363">13 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7364">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7364">11 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7365">две контрольные цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7365">two check digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7366">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7366">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7367">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7367">yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7368">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7368">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7369">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7369">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7370">Функция  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7370">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7371">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7371">A keyword from  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7372">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7372">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7373">Функция  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7373">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 


```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg National Identification Number (Natural persons) -->
      <Entity id="aaf661ed-29ec-426d-8bf9-880cad298ebb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="luxemburg-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7396">Номер паспорта Луксембург</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7396">Luxemburg passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7397">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7397">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7398">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7398">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7399">восемь цифр или букв без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7399">eight digits or letters with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7400">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7400">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7401">восемь цифр или букв (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7401">eight digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7402">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7402">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7403">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7403">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7404">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7404">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7405">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7405">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7406">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_nation_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7406">The regular expression  `Regex_nation_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7407">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_nation_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7407">A keyword from  `Keywords_nation_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_nation_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_nation_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7408">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7408">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_nation_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7409">Keywords_nation_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7409">Keywords_nation_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7410">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7410">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7411">номер паспорта для Латвии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7411">latvian passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7412">паспорт нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7412">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7413">пасснуммер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7413">passnummer</span></span>

## <a name="luxemburg-national-identification-number-non-natural-persons"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7414">Луксембург Национальный идентификационный номер (неестественные пользователи)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7414">Luxemburg national identification number (non natural persons)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7415">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7415">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7416">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7416">11 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7417">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7417">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7418">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7418">11 digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7419">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7419">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7420">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7420">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7421">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7421">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7422">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7422">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7423">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7423">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7424">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7424">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7425">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7425">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7426">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7426">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7427">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7427">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7428">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7428">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7429">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7429">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7430">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7430">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7431">Функция  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7431">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7432">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7432">A keyword from  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7433">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7433">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7434">Функция  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7434">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg National Identification Number (Non-natural persons) -->
      <Entity id="84bffa3a-d805-4788-a613-b1e4df3804cf" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="malaysia-identification-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7474">Идентификационный номер карты Малайзии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7474">Malaysia identification card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7475">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7475">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7476">12 цифр, содержащих необязательные дефисы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7476">12 digits containing optional hyphens</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7477">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7477">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7478">12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7478">12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7479">шесть цифр в формате ГГММДД Дата рождения;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7479">six digits in the format YYMMDD which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7480">тире (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7480">a dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7481">код места рождения из двух букв</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7481">two-letter place-of-birth code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7482">тире (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7482">a dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7483">три случайные цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7483">three random digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7484">код пола из одной цифры;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7484">one-digit gender code</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7485">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7485">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7486">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7486">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7487">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7487">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7488">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7488">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7489">регулярное выражение Regex_malaysia_id_card_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7489">The regular expression Regex_malaysia_id_card_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7490">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7490">A keyword from Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Malaysia ID Card Number -->
</Entity>
      <Entity id="7f0e921c-9677-435b-aba2-bb8f1013c749" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
            <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malaysia_id_card_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7491">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7491">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_malaysia_id_card_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7492">Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7492">Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7493">карточка цифрового приложения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7493">digital application card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7494">i/c</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7494">i/c</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7495">i/c нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7495">i/c no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7496">внутренних</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7496">ic</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7497">МФ нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7497">ic no</span></span>
