## <a name="malta-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7517">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера Мальта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7517">Malta driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7518">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7518">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7519">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7519">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7520">Сочетание двух символов и шести цифр в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7520">Combination of two characters and six digits in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7521">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7521">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7522">сочетание двух символов и шести цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7522">combination of two characters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7523">два символа (цифры или буквы без учета регистра);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7523">two characters (digits or letters, not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7524">пробел (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7524">a space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7525">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7525">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7526">пробел (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7526">a space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7527">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7527">three digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7528">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7528">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7529">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7529">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7530">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7530">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7531">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7531">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7532">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7532">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7533">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` или `Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7533">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="a3bdaa4a-8371-4735-8fa5-56ee0fb4afc4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="malta-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7657">Номер идентификационной карточки Мальта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7657">Malta identity card number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7658">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7658">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7659">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7659">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7660">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7660">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7661">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7661">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7662">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7662">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7663">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7663">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7664">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7664">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7665">семь цифр, за которыми следует одна буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7665">seven digits followed by one letter</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7666">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7666">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7667">семь цифр, за которыми следует одна буква:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7667">seven digits followed by one letter:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7668">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7668">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7669">одна буква в письмах "M, G, A, P, L, H, B, Z" (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7669">one letter in "M, G, A, P, L, H, B, Z" (case insensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7670">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7670">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7671">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7671">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7672">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7672">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7673">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7673">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7674">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7674">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7675">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7675">A keyword from  `Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7676">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7676">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7677">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7677">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Identity Card Number -->
      <Entity id="854b36b3-a388-4ac8-a4ec-677c2b5e4356" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="malta-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7694">Номер паспорта для Мальта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7694">Malta passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7695">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7695">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7696">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7696">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7697">семь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7697">seven digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7698">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7698">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7699">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7699">seven digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7700">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7700">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7701">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7701">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7702">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7702">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7703">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7703">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7704">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7704">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7705">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` или `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7705">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` or `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="malta-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7722">Идентификационный номер налога Мальта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7722">Malta tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7723">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7723">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7724">Для национальных Мальтийский:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7724">For Maltese nationals:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7725">семь цифр и одна буква в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7725">seven digits and one letter in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7726">Мальтийскийные страны и Мальтийский, не являющиеся субъектами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7726">Non-Maltese nationals and Maltese entities:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7727">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7727">nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7728">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7728">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7729">Мальтийский Nationals: семь цифр и одна буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7729">Maltese nationals: seven digits and one letter</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7730">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7730">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7731">одна буква (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7731">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7732">Мальтийскийные страны и Мальтийский, не связанные с организациями: девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7732">Non-Maltese nationals and Maltese entities: nine digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7733">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7733">nine digits</span></span> 
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7734">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7734">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7735">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7735">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7736">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7736">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7737">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7737">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7738">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number`  или `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` ищет содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7738">The regex  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number`  or `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7739">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7739">A keyword from  `Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7740">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7740">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7741">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number` или `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` ищет содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7741">The regex  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number` or `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Tax ID Number -->
      <Entity id="ec830c63-65f4-45d0-9d8c-910dc8334b20" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-citizens-service-bsn-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7774">Номер службы (BSN) для Нидерландов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7774">Netherlands citizen's service (BSN) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7775">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7775">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7776">восемь девяти цифр, содержащих необязательные пробелы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7776">eight-nine digits containing optional spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7777">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7777">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7778">восемь девяти цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7778">eight-nine digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7779">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7779">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7780">пробел (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7780">a space (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7781">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7781">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7782">пробел (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7782">a space (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7783">две три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7783">two-three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7784">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7784">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7785">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7785">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7786">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7786">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7787">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7787">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7788">функция Func_netherlands_bsn находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7788">The function Func_netherlands_bsn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7789">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_netherlands_bsn;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7789">A keyword from Keyword_netherlands_bsn is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7790">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7790">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Citizen's Service (BSN) Number -->
      <Entity id="c5f54253-ef7e-44f6-a578-440ed67e946d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_bsn" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7811">уникальный идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7811">unique identification number</span></span>

## <a name="netherlands-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7814">Номер водительского удостоверения для Нидерландов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7814">Netherlands driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7815">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7815">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7816">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7816">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7817">десять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7817">ten digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7818">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7818">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7819">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7819">ten digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7820">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7820">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7821">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7821">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7822">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7822">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7823">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7823">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7824">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7824">The regular expression  `Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7825">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` или `Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7825">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="6247fbea-ab80-4be5-8233-308b7c031401" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7826">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7826">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_drivers_license_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7827">Keywords_eu_driver "s_license_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7827">Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7828">дриверлик</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7828">driverlic</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7829">дриверликс</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7829">driverlics</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7830">дриверлиценсе</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7830">driverlicense</span></span>

## <a name="netherlands-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7953">Номер паспорта Нидерландов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7953">Netherlands passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7954">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7954">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7955">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7955">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7956">девять букв или цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7956">nine letters or digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7957">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7957">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7958">девять букв или цифр;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7958">nine letters or digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7959">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7959">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7960">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7960">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7961">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7961">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7962">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7962">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7963">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7963">The regular expression  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7964">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7964">A keyword from  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7974">Идентификационный номер налога Нидерландов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7974">Netherlands tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7975">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7975">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7976">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7976">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7977">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7977">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7978">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7978">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7979">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7979">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7980">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7980">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7981">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7981">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7982">девять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7982">nine digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7983">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7983">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7984">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7984">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7985">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7985">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7986">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7986">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-7987">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7987">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7988">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7988">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7989">Функция  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7989">The function  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7990">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7990">A keyword from  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-7991">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7991">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-7992">Функция  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-7992">The function  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="01f42a64-eba7-4892-a67b-398237e4ade2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8030">Номер налога добавленных значений в Нидерландов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8030">Netherlands value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8031">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8031">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8032">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8032">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8033">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8033">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8034">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8034">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8035">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8035">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8036">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8036">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8037">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8037">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8038">14-буквенно-буквенно-цифровой шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8038">14 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8039">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8039">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8040">14-буквенно-буквенно-символьный шаблон:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8040">14-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8041">N или n</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8041">N or n</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8042">L или l</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8042">L or l</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8043">необязательный пробел, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8043">optional space, dot or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8044">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8044">nine digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8045">необязательный пробел, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8045">optional space, dot or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8046">B или b</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8046">B or b</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8047">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8047">two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8048">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8048">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8049">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8049">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8050">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8050">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8051">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8051">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8052">Функция Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8052">The function Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8053">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_netherlands_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8053">A keyword from Keywords_netherlands_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8054">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8054">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8055">Функция Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8055">The function Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="4f320d9b-4972-41ae-b337-88d499bb1ade" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="new-zealand-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8064">Номер банковского счета Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8064">New Zealand bank account number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8065">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8065">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8066">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8066">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8067">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8067">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8068">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8068">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8069">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8069">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8070">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8070">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8071">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8071">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8072">шаблон с 14 до 16 цифр с необязательным разделителем</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8072">14 to 16 digit pattern with optional delimiter</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8073">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8073">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8074">шаблон с 14 до 16 цифр с необязательным разделителем:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8074">14 to 16 digit pattern with optional delimiter:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8075">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8075">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8076">Необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8076">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8077">от трех до четырех цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8077">three to four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8078">Необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8078">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8079">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8079">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8080">Необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8080">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8081">две до трех цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8081">two to three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8082">Параметры дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8082">an options hyphen or space</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8083">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8083">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8084">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8084">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8085">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8085">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8086">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8086">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8087">Функция Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8087">The function Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8088">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_new_zealand_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8088">A keyword from Keywords_new_zealand_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8089">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8089">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8090">Функция Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8090">The function Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- New Zealand Bank Account Number -->
      <Entity id="1a97fc2b-dd2f-48f1-bc4e-2ddf25813956" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_new_zFealand_bank_account_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8093">account number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8093">account number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8096">bank_acct_branch</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8096">bank_acct_branch</span></span>

## <a name="new-zealand-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8098">Номер водительского удостоверения для Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8098">New Zealand driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8099">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8099">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8100">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8100">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8101">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8101">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8102">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8102">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8103">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8103">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8104">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8104">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8105">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8105">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8106">8-буквенно-цифровой шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8106">eight character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8107">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8107">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8108">8-буквенно-цифровой шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8108">eight character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8109">две буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8109">two letters</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8110">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8110">six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8111">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8111">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8112">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8112">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8113">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8113">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8114">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8114">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8115">Функция Func_newzealand_driver_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8115">The function Func_newzealand_driver_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8116">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_newzealand_driver_license_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8116">A keyword from Keywords_newzealand_driver_license_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8117">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8117">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8118">Функция Func_newzealand_driver_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8118">The function Func_newzealand_driver_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- New Zealand Driver License Number -->
      <Entity id="1924b377-d287-49c9-a737-cfe7a8a2615a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_driver_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_newzealand_driver_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_driver_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="new-zealand-inland-revenue-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8185">Номер дохода по некоторому контакту для Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8185">New Zealand inland revenue number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8186">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8186">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8187">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8187">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8188">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8188">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8189">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8189">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8190">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8190">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8191">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8191">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8192">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8192">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8193">восемь или девять цифр с необязательными ограничителями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8193">eight or nine digits with optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8194">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8194">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8195">восемь или девять цифр с необязательными ограничителями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8195">eight or nine digits with optional delimiters</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8196">две или три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8196">two or three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8197">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8197">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8198">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8198">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8199">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8199">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8200">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8200">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8201">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8201">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8202">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8202">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8203">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8203">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8204">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8204">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8205">Функция Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8205">The function Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8206">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8206">A keyword from Keywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8207">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8207">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8208">Функция Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8208">The function Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- New Zealand Inland Revenue Number -->
      <Entity id="dd0fe2bc-7bcf-455f-bac1-83b1e3eb25fd" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8209">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8209">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8210">Keyword_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8210">Keyword_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8211">ИРД но.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8211">ird no.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8212">ИРД нет #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8212">ird no#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8213">NZ ИРД</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8213">nz ird</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8214">Новая Зеландия ИРД</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8214">new zealand ird</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8215">номер ИРД</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8215">ird number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8216">номер дохода на землю</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8216">inland revenue number</span></span>


## <a name="new-zealand-ministry-of-health-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8217">Номер министерства здоровья Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8217">New Zealand ministry of health number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8218">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8218">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8219">три буквы, пробел (необязательно) и четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8219">three letters, a space (optional), and four digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8220">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8220">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8221">три буквы (без учета регистра), пробел (необязательно) из четырех цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8221">three letters (not case sensitive) a space (optional) four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8222">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8222">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8223">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8223">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8224">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8224">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8225">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8225">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8226">функция Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8226">The function Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8227">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_nz_terms;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8227">A keyword from Keyword_nz_terms is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8228">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8228">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- New Zealand Health Number -->
<Entity id="2b71c1c8-d14e-4430-82dc-fd1ed6bf05c7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_nz_terms" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8229">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8229">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_nz_terms"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8230">Keyword_nz_terms</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8230">Keyword_nz_terms</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8231">нхи</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8231">NHI</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8232">Новая Зеландия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8232">New Zealand</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8233">Здравоохранение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8233">Health</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8234">обращения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8234">treatment</span></span> 


## <a name="new-zealand-social-wlefare-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8235">Номер социального влефареа Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8235">New Zealand social wlefare number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8236">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8236">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8237">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8237">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8238">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8238">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8239">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8239">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8240">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8240">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8241">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8241">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8242">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8242">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8243">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8243">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8244">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8244">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8245">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8245">nine digits</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8246">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8246">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8247">Необязательный перенос</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8247">an optional hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8248">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8248">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8249">Необязательный перенос</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8249">an optional hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8250">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8250">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8251">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8251">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8252">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8252">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8253">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8253">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8254">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8254">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8255">Функция Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8255">The function Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8256">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8256">A keyword from Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8257">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8257">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8258">Функция Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8258">The function Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Newzealand Social Welfare Number -->
      <Entity id="20f3c48d-4ac1-4cd2-86bd-34ecc1826e9d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
    </Version>
```

## <a name="norway-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8266">Идентификационный номер Норвегии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8266">Norway identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8267">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8267">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8268">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8268">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8269">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8269">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8270">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8270">11 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8271">шесть цифр в формате ддммгг — Дата рождения;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8271">six digits in the format DDMMYY which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8272">индивидуальный номер из трех цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8272">three-digit individual number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8273">две контрольные цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8273">two check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8274">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8274">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8275">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8275">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8276">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8276">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8277">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8277">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8278">функция Func_norway_id_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8278">The function Func_norway_id_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8279">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_norway_id_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8279">A keyword from Keyword_norway_id_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8280">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8280">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8281">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8281">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8282">функция Func_norway_id_numbe находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8282">The function Func_norway_id_numbe finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8283">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8283">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Norway Identification Number -->
<Entity id="d4c8a798-e9f2-4bd3-9652-500d24080fc3" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_norway_id_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_norway_id_number"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_norway_id_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="philippines-unified-multi-purpose-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8292">Идентификационный номер единой системы для различных целей Филиппины</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8292">Philippines unified multi-purpose identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8293">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8293">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8294">12 цифр, разделенных дефисами.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8294">12 digits separated by hyphens</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8295">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8295">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8296">12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8296">12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8297">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8297">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8298">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8298">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8299">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8299">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8300">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8300">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8301">одна цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8301">one digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8302">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8302">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8303">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8303">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8304">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8304">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8305">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8305">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8306">регулярное выражение Regex_philippines_unified_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8306">The regular expression Regex_philippines_unified_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8307">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_philippines_id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8307">A keyword from Keyword_philippines_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Philippines Unified Multi-Purpose ID number -->
<Entity id="019b39dd-8c25-4765-91a3-d9c6baf3c3b3" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_philippines_unified_id"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_philippines_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8308">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8308">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_philippines_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8309">Keyword_philippines_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8309">Keyword_philippines_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8310">Unified Multi-Purpose ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8310">Unified Multi-Purpose ID</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8311">умид</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8311">UMID</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8312">Identity Card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8312">Identity Card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8313">Pinag-isang Multi-Layunin ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8313">Pinag-isang Multi-Layunin ID</span></span>

## <a name="poland-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8314">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8314">Poland driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8315">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8315">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8316">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8316">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8317">14 цифр, содержащих 2 косых черты.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8317">14 digits containing 2 forward slashes</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8318">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8318">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8319">14 цифр и 2 косых черт:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8319">14 digits and 2 forward slashes:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8320">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8320">five digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8321">косая черта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8321">a forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8322">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8322">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8323">косая черта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8323">a forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8324">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8324">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8325">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8325">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8326">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8326">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8327">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8327">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8328">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8328">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8329">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8329">The regular expression  `Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8330">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` или `Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8330">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Poland Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="24d51f99-ee9e-4060-a077-cae58cab1ee4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
