## <a name="poland-identity-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8454">Идентификационная карточка Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8454">Poland identity card</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8455">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8455">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8456">три буквы и шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8456">three letters and six digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8457">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8457">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8458">три буквы (без учета регистра), за которыми следуют шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8458">three letters (not case sensitive) followed by six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8459">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8459">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8460">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8460">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8461">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8461">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8462">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8462">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8463">функция Func_polish_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8463">The function Func_polish_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8464">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8464">A keyword from Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8465">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8465">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Poland Identity Card-->
<Entity id="25E64989-ED5D-40CA-A939-6C14183BB7BF" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_national_id" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number" />
      </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8466">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8466">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8467">Keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8467">Keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8468">Довóд особисти</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8468">Dowód osobisty</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8469">Нумер доводу особистего</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8469">Numer dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8470">Назва i нумер доводу особистего</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8470">Nazwa i numer dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8471">Назва i НР доводу особистего</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8471">Nazwa i nr dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8472">Nazwa i nr dowodu tożsamości</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8472">Nazwa i nr dowodu tożsamości</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8473">Dowód Tożsamości</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8473">Dowód Tożsamości</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8474">Dow.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8474">dow.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8475">совместим.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8475">os.</span></span>

   
## <a name="poland-national-id-pesel"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8476">Национальный идентификатор Польша (PESEL)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8476">Poland national ID (PESEL)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8477">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8477">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8478">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8478">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8479">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8479">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8480">6 цифр, представляющих дату рождения, в формате ГГММДД.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8480">6 digits representing date of birth in the format YYMMDD</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8481">4 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8481">4 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8482">1 контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8482">1 check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8483">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8483">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8484">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8484">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8485">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8485">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8486">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8486">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8487">функция Func_pesel_identification_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8487">The function Func_pesel_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8488">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_pesel_identification_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8488">A keyword from Keyword_pesel_identification_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8489">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8489">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8490">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8490">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8491">функция Func_pesel_identification_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8491">The function Func_pesel_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8492">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8492">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Poland National ID (PESEL) -->
      <Entity id="E3AAF206-4297-412F-9E06-BA8487E22456" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_pesel_identification_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_pesel_identification_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_pesel_identification_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="poland-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8504">Номер паспорта для Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8504">Poland passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8505">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включен в тип конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8505">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8506">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8506">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8507">две буквы и семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8507">two letters and seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8508">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8508">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8509">Две буквы (без учета регистра), за которыми следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8509">Two letters (not case sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8510">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8510">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8511">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8511">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8512">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8512">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8513">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8513">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8514">функция Func_polish_passport_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8514">The function Func_polish_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8515">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8515">A keyword from Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8516">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8516">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Poland Passport Number -->
<Entity id="03937FB5-D2B6-4487-B61F-0F8BFF7C3517" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number" />
      </Pattern>
</Entity>
</Version>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8517">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8517">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8518">Keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8518">Keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8519">Нумер пасзпорту</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8519">Numer paszportu</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8520">НР.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8520">Nr.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8521">пасзпорту</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8521">Paszportu</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8522">пасзпорт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8522">Paszport</span></span>

## <a name="poland-regon-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8523">Номер РЕГОНа Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8523">Poland REGON number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8524">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8524">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8525">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8525">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8526">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8526">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8527">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8527">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8528">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8528">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8529">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8529">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8530">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8530">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8531">девять цифр или номер из 14 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8531">nine digit or 14 digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8532">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8532">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8533">девять цифр или 14 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8533">nine digit or 14-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8534">девять цифр или</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8534">nine digits or</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8535">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8535">nine digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8536">дискрецион</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8536">hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8537">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8537">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8538">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8538">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8539">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8539">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8540">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8540">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8541">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8541">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8542">Функция Func_polish_regon_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8542">The function Func_polish_regon_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8543">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_polish_regon_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8543">A keyword from Keywords_polish_regon_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8544">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8544">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8545">Функция Func_polish_regon_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8545">The function Func_polish_regon_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Polish REGON Number  -->
      <Entity id="fc87b421-f437-4f8b-b739-29a735ead0d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_regon_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_polish_regon_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_regon_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="poland-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8562">Идентификационный номер для таможенного учета Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8562">Poland tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8563">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8563">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8564">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8564">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8565">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8565">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8566">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8566">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8567">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8567">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8568">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8568">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8569">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8569">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8570">11 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8570">11 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8571">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8571">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8572">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8572">11 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8573">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8573">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8574">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8574">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8575">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8575">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8576">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8576">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8577">Функция  `Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8577">The function  `Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8578">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8578">A keyword from  `Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
  
```xml
      <!-- Poland Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="1ff28b4d-40f2-49e9-b677-9606a88e2bca" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-citizen-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8608">Номер карточки с префиксом "Португалия"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8608">Portugal citizen card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8609">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8609">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8610">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8610">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8611">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8611">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8612">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8612">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8613">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8613">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8614">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8614">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8615">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8615">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8616">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8616">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8617">регулярное выражение Regex_portugal_citizen_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8617">The regular expression Regex_portugal_citizen_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8618">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_portugal_citizen_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8618">A keyword from Keyword_portugal_citizen_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Portugal Citizen Card Number -->
<Entity id="91a7ece2-add4-4986-9a15-c84544d81ecd" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_citizen_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_portugal_citizen_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8638">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера Португалия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8638">Portugal driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8639">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8639">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8640">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8640">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8641">два образца — две буквы, за которыми следуют 5-8 цифр со специальными символами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8641">two patterns - two letters followed by 5-8 digits with special characters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8642">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8642">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8643">Pattern 1: две буквы, за которыми следует 5/6 со специальными символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8643">Pattern 1: Two letters followed by 5/6 with special characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8644">Две буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8644">Two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8645">дефис;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8645">A hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8646">Пять или шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8646">Five or Six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8647">Пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8647">A space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8648">Одна цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8648">One digit</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8649">Шаблон 2: одна буква, за которой следуют 6/8 цифры со специальными символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8649">Pattern 2: One letter followed by 6/8 digits with special characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8650">Одна буква (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8650">One letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8651">дефис;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8651">A hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8652">Шесть или восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8652">Six or eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8653">Пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8653">A space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8654">одна цифра.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8654">One digit</span></span>

    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8655">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8655">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8656">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8656">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8657">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8657">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8658">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8658">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8659">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8659">The regular expression  `Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8660">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` или `Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8660">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Portugal Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="977f1e5a-2c33-4bcc-b516-95bb275cff23" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8792">Номер паспорта для Португалия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8792">Portugal passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8793">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8793">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8794">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8794">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8795">одна буква, за которой следуют шесть цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8795">one letter followed by six digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8796">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8796">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8797">одна буква, за которой следуют шесть цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8797">one letter followed by six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8798">одна буква (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8798">one letter (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8799">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8799">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8800">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8800">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8801">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8801">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8802">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8802">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8803">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8803">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8804">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8804">The regular expression  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8805">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` или `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8805">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` or `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8829">Идентификационный номер для налога на Португалия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8829">Portugal tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8830">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8830">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8831">девять цифр с необязательными пробелами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8831">nine digits with optional spaces</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8832">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8832">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8833">3 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8833">3 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8834">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8834">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8835">3 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8835">3 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8836">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8836">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8837">3 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8837">3 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8838">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8838">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8839">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8839">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8840">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8840">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8841">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8841">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8842">Функция  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8842">The function  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8843">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8843">A keyword from  `Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8844">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8844">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8845">Функция  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8845">The function  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Portugal Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="65372402-3131-4f1e-9983-4439841d1f15" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
```

## <a name="romania-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8870">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера Румыния</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8870">Romania driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8871">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8871">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8872">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8872">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8873">один символ, за которым следуют восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8873">one character followed by eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8874">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8874">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8875">один символ, за которым следуют восемь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8875">one character followed by eight digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8876">одна буква (без учета регистра) или цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8876">one letter (not case-sensitive) or digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8877">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8877">eight digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8878">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8878">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8879">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8879">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-8880">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8880">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-8881">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8881">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8882">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8882">The regular expression  `Regex_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-8883">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` или `Keywords_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-8883">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Romania Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="b5511ace-2fd8-4ae4-b6fc-c7c6e4689e3c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_romania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="romania-personal-numeric-code-cnp"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-9011">Персональный числовой код Румыния (КНП)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9011">Romania personal numeric code (CNP)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-9012">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9012">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9013">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9013">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9014">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9014">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9015">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9015">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9016">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9016">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9017">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9017">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-9018">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9018">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-9019">13 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9019">13 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-9020">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9020">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9021">1 цифра из 1-9</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9021">1 digit from 1-9</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9022">6 цифр, представляющих дату рождения (ГГММДД)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9022">6 digits representing date of birth (YYMMDD)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9023">2 цифры, которые могут быть 01-52 или 99</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9023">2 digits which can be 01-52 or 99</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9024">4 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9024">4 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-9025">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9025">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-9026">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9026">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-9027">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9027">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-9028">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9028">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9029">Функция  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9029">The function  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9030">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9030">A keyword from  `Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-9031">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9031">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9032">Функция  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9032">The function  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Romania Personal Numerical Code (CNP) -->
      <Entity id="eb5fa399-fe28-4c67-8188-d63a616ed89c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="romania-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-9083">Номер паспорта для Румыния</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9083">Romania passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-9084">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9084">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-9085">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9085">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-9086">восемь или девять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9086">eight or nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-9087">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9087">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-9088">восемь или девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9088">eight or nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-9089">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9089">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-9090">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9090">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-9091">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9091">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-9092">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9092">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9093">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_romania_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9093">The regular expression  `Regex_romania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9094">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` или `Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9094">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` or `Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_romania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9111">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9111">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9112">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9112">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9113">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9113">information governance</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-9116">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9116">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-9117">номер из десяти цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9117">ten digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-9118">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9118">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-9119">номер из десяти цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9119">ten digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9120">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9120">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9121">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9121">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9122">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9122">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9123">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9123">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9124">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9124">six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-9125">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9125">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-9126">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9126">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-9127">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9127">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-9128">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9128">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9129">Регулярное выражение Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_Domestic находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9129">The regex Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_Domestic finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9130">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9130">A keyword from Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Russian Passport Number Domestic -->
      <Entity id="76ec2f5d-cedb-48e1-8070-1998794af445" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_Domestic" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="saudi-arabia-national-id"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-9183">Национальный идентификатор для Саудовской Аравии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9183">Saudi Arabia National ID</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-9184">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9184">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-9185">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9185">ten digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-9186">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9186">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-9187">десять последовательных цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9187">ten consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-9188">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9188">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-9189">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9189">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-9190">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9190">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-9191">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9191">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9192">регулярное выражение Regex_saudi_arabia_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9192">The regular expression Regex_saudi_arabia_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9193">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9193">A keyword from Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Saudi Arabia National ID -->
<Entity id="8c5a0ba8-404a-41a3-8871-746aa21ee6c0" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_saudi_arabia_national_id" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="singapore-national-registration-identity-card-nric-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-9200">Номер национальной идентификационной карточки для регистрации (NRIC), Сингапур</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9200">Singapore national registration identity card (NRIC) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-9201">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9201">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-9202">девять букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9202">nine letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-9203">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9203">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9204">девять букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9204">nine letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9205">буква "F", "G", "S" или "T" (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9205">the letter "F", "G", "S", or "T" (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9206">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9206">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9207">цифра алфавитной проверки</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9207">an alphabetic check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-9208">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9208">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-9209">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9209">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-9210">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9210">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-9211">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9211">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9212">регулярное выражение Regex_singapore_nric находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9212">The regular expression Regex_singapore_nric finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9213">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_singapore_nric;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9213">A keyword from Keyword_singapore_nric is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9214">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9214">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-9215">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9215">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9216">регулярное выражение Regex_singapore_nric находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9216">The regular expression Regex_singapore_nric finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9217">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9217">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Singapore National Registration Identity Card (NRIC) Number -->
<Entity id="cead390a-dd83-4856-9751-fb6dc98c34da" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_singapore_nric"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_singapore_nric"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_singapore_nric"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="slovakia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-9228">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера Словакия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9228">Slovakia driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-9229">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9229">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-9230">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9230">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-9231">один символ, за которым следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9231">one character followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-9232">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9232">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-9233">один символ, за которым следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9233">one character followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9234">одна буква (без учета регистра) или цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9234">one letter (not case-sensitive) or digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9235">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9235">seven digits</span></span> 
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-9236">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9236">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-9237">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9237">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-9238">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9238">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-9239">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9239">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9240">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9240">The regular expression  `Regex_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9241">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` или `Keywords_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9241">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovakia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="14240c22-b6de-4ce5-a90b-137f74252513" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="slovakia-personal-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-9367">Словакия персональный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9367">Slovakia personal number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-9368">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9368">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9369">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9369">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9370">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9370">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9371">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9371">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9372">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9372">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9373">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9373">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-9374">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9374">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-9375">девять или десять цифр, содержащих необязательную обратную косую черту</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9375">nine or ten digits containing optional backslash</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-9376">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9376">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9377">6 цифр, представляющих дату рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9377">6 digits representing date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9378">Необязательная косая черта (/)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9378">optional slash (/)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9379">3 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9379">3 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9380">1 обязательная контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9380">1 optional check digit</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-9381">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9381">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-9382">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9382">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-9383">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9383">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-9384">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9384">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9385">Функция  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9385">The function  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9386">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9386">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-9387">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9387">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9388">Функция  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9388">The function  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovakia Personal Number -->
      <Entity id="951c26b7-3b35-4f73-924b-15dd599cb9ab" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
    </Version>
```

## <a name="slovakia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-9435">Словакия — номер паспорта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9435">Slovakia passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-9436">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9436">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-9437">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9437">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-9438">одна цифра или буква, за которой следуют семь цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9438">one digit or letter followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-9439">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9439">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-9440">одна цифра или буква (без учета регистра), за которой следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9440">one digit or letter (not case sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-9441">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9441">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-9442">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9442">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-9443">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9443">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-9444">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9444">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9445">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9445">The regular expression  `Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9446">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` или `Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9446">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` or `Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="slovenia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-9465">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера Словения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9465">Slovenia driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-9466">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в типе конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9466">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-9467">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9467">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-9468">девять цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9468">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-9469">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9469">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-9470">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9470">nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-9471">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9471">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-9472">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9472">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-9473">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9473">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-9474">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9474">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9475">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9475">The regular expression  `Regex_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9476">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` или `Keywords_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9476">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovenia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="d5bc089a-f2ee-433d-a6b1-5c253051d6f2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="slovenia-unique-master-citizen-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-9603">Словения уникальный номер хозяина</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9603">Slovenia Unique Master Citizen Number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-9604">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9604">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9605">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9605">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9606">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9606">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9607">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9607">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9608">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9608">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9609">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9609">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-9610">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9610">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-9611">13 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9611">13 digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-9612">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9612">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-9613">13 цифр в указанном шаблоне:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9613">13 digits in the specified pattern:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9614">семь цифр, которые соответствуют дате рождения (ДДММЛЛЛ), где "ЛЛЛ" соответствует последним трем цифрам года рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9614">seven digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMLLL) where "LLL" corresponds to the last three digits of the birth year</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9615">две цифры, соответствующие области рождения "50"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9615">two digits that correspond to the area of birth "50"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9616">три цифры, которые соответствуют сочетанию пола и серийного номера для людей, которые приставили один и тот же день (000-499 для пола и 500-999 для розетки)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9616">three digits that correspond to a combination of gender and serial number for persons born on the same day (000-499 for male and 500-999 for female)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9617">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9617">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-9618">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9618">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-9619">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9619">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-9620">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9620">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-9621">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9621">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9622">Функция  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9622">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9623">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9623">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-9624">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9624">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-9625">Функция  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-9625">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovenia Unique Master Citizen Number -->
      <Entity id="68948b27-803d-41e4-adf1-13e05eb541bb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
