## <a name="swift-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10459">Код SWIFT</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10459">SWIFT code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10460">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10460">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10461">четыре буквы, за которыми следует 5-31 букв или цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10461">four letters followed by 5-31 letters or digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10462">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10462">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10463">четыре буквы, за которыми следует 5-31 букв или цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10463">four letters followed by 5-31 letters or digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10464">код банка из четырех букв (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10464">four-letter bank code (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10465">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10465">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10466">4–28 букв или цифр (основной номер банковского счета, BBAN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10466">4-28 letters or digits (the Basic Bank Account Number (BBAN))</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10467">необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10467">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10468">одна – три буквы или цифры (остаток от BBAN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10468">one to three letters or digits (remainder of the BBAN)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10469">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10469">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10470">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10470">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10471">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10471">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10472">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10472">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10473">регулярное выражение Regex_swift находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10473">The regular expression Regex_swift finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10474">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_swift.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10474">A keyword from Keyword_swift is found.</span></span>

```xml
<Entity id="cb2ab58c-9cb8-4c81-baf8-a4e106791df4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_swift" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_swift" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="switzerland-ssn-ahv-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10511">Номер АХВа для Швейцарии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10511">Switzerland SSN AHV number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10512">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10512">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10513">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10513">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10514">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10514">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10515">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10515">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10516">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10516">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10517">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10517">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10518">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10518">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10519">13 цифра, цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10519">13 digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10520">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10520">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10521">13 цифра:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10521">13 digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10522">три цифры — 756</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10522">three digits - 756</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10523">Необязательная точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10523">an optional dot</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10524">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10524">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10525">Необязательная точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10525">an optional dot</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10526">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10526">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10527">Необязательная точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10527">an optional dot</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10528">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10528">two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10529">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10529">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10530">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10530">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10531">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10531">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10532">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10532">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10533">Функция Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10533">The function Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10534">Найдено ключевое слово из Keywords_swiss_social_security_number_ahv.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10534">A keyword from Keywords_swiss_social_security_number_ahv is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10535">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10535">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10536">Функция Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10536">The function Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Swiss SSN AHV Number -->
      <Entity id="277cfa4b-6eaa-4a1b-9492-099dec849971" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_swiss_social_security_number_ahv" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="taiwan-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10557">Национальный идентификационный номер для Тайваня</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10557">Taiwan national identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10558">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10558">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10559">одна буква (на английском языке), за которой следуют девять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10559">one letter (in English) followed by nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10560">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10560">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10561">одна буква (на английском языке), за которой следуют девять цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10561">one letter (in English) followed by nine digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10562">одна буква (на английском языке, без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10562">one letter (in English, not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10563">цифра "1" или "2"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10563">the digit "1" or "2"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10564">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10564">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10565">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10565">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10566">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10566">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10567">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10567">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10568">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10568">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10569">функция Func_taiwanese_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10569">The function Func_taiwanese_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10570">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_taiwanese_national_id;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10570">A keyword from Keyword_taiwanese_national_id is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10571">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10571">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10572">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10572">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10573">функция Func_taiwanese_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10573">The function Func_taiwanese_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10574">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10574">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Taiwanese National ID -->
<Entity id="4C7BFC34-8DD1-421D-8FB7-6C6182C2AF03" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_taiwanese_national_id" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_taiwanese_national_id" />
      </Pattern>
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
         <IdMatch idRef="Func_taiwanese_national_id" />
       </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="taiwan-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10591">Номер паспорта для Тайваня</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10591">Taiwan passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10592">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10592">Format</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10593">номер биометрического паспорта: девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10593">biometric passport number: nine digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10594">номер биометрической службы Passport: девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10594">non-biometric passport number: nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10595">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10595">Pattern</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10596">номер биометрического паспорта:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10596">biometric passport number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10597">символ "3"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10597">the character "3"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10598">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10598">eight digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10599">номер биометрической службы Passport:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10599">non-biometric passport number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10600">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10600">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10601">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10601">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10602">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10602">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10603">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10603">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10604">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10604">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10605">регулярное выражение Regex_taiwan_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10605">The regular expression Regex_taiwan_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10606">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_taiwan_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10606">A keyword from Keyword_taiwan_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Taiwan Passport Number -->
<Entity id="e7251cb4-4c2c-41df-963e-924eb3dae04a" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_taiwan_passport"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_taiwan_passport"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="taiwan-resident-certificate-arctarc-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10617">Номер сертификата резидента (ARC/TARC) для Тайваня</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10617">Taiwan resident certificate (ARC/TARC) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10618">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10618">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10619">десять букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10619">ten letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10620">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10620">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10621">десять букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10621">ten letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10622">две буквы (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10622">two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10623">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10623">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10624">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10624">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10625">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10625">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10626">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10626">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10627">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10627">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10628">регулярное выражение Regex_taiwan_resident_certificate находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10628">The regular expression Regex_taiwan_resident_certificate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10629">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10629">A keyword from Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Taiwan Resident Certificate (ARC/TARC) -->
<Entity id="48269fec-05ea-46ea-b326-f5623a58c6e9" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_taiwan_resident_certificate"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10630">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10630">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10631">Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10631">Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10632">Resident Certificate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10632">Resident Certificate</span></span>

## <a name="thai-population-identification-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10643">Код идентификации для тайского заполнения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10643">Thai population identification code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10644">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10644">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10645">13 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10645">13 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10646">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10646">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10647">13 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10647">13 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10648">Первая цифра не равна нулю или девять</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10648">first digit is not zero  or nine</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10649">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10649">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10650">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10650">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10651">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10651">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10652">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10652">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10653">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10653">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10654">Функция Func_Thai_Citizen_Id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10654">The function Func_Thai_Citizen_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10655">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_Thai_Citizen_Id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10655">A keyword from Keyword_Thai_Citizen_Id is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10656">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10656">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10657">Функция Func_Thai_Citizen_Id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10657">The function Func_Thai_Citizen_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Thai Citizen ID -->
-<Entity id="44ca9e86-ead7-4c5d-884a-e2eaa401515e" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10663">รหัสบัตรประชาชน</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10663">รหัสบัตรประชาชน</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10664">บัตรประชาชน</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10664">บัตรประชาชน</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10665">รหัสบัตรประชาชน</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10665">รหัสบัตรประชาชน</span></span>
  
## <a name="turkish-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10666">Турецкий национальный идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10666">Turkish national identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10667">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10667">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10668">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10668">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10669">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10669">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10670">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10670">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10671">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10671">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10672">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10672">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10673">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10673">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10674">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10674">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10675">Функция Func_Turkish_National_Id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10675">The function Func_Turkish_National_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10676">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_Turkish_National_Id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10676">A keyword from Keyword_Turkish_National_Id is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10677">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10677">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10678">Функция Func_Turkish_National_Id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10678">The function Func_Turkish_National_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Turkish National Identity -->
-<Entity id="fb621f20-3876-4cfc-acec-8c8e73ca32c7" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Turkish_National_Id"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_Turkish_National_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Turkish_National_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10679">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10679">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_turkish_national_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10680">Keyword_turkish_national_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10680">Keyword_turkish_national_id</span></span>

## <a name="uk-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10685">Королевств</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10685">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10686">номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10686">driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10687">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включен в тип конфиденциальной информации номера лицензии для драйвера ЕС и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10687">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10688">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10688">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10689">Сочетание 18 букв и цифр в указанном формате.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10689">Combination of 18 letters and digits in the specified format</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10690">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10690">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10691">18 букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10691">18 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10692">пять букв (без учета регистра) или цифра 9 вместо буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10692">five letters (not case sensitive) or the digit "9" in place of a letter</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10693">одна цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10693">one digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10694">пять цифр в формате даты ММДДИ для даты рождения (седьмой символ увеличивается на 50, если драйвер — гнездо, то есть 51 – 62, а не с 01 – 12)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10694">five digits in the date format MMDDY for date of birth (7th character is incremented by 50 if driver is female, i.e. 51 to 62 instead of 01 to 12)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10695">две буквы (без учета регистра) или цифра "9" вместо буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10695">two letters (not case sensitive) or the digit "9" in place of a letter</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10696">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10696">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10697">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10697">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10698">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10698">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10699">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10699">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10700">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10700">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10701">функция Func_uk_drivers_license находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10701">The function Func_uk_drivers_license finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10702">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_drivers_license;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10702">A keyword from Keyword_uk_drivers_license is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10703">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10703">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.K. Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="f93de4be-d94c-40df-a8be-461738047551" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_drivers_license" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_drivers_license" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10720">dual control car</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10720">dual control car</span></span> 
   
## <a name="uk-electoral-roll-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10721">Королевств</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10721">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10722">номер рулона електорал</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10722">electoral roll number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10723">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10723">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10724">две буквы, за которыми следуют 1-4 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10724">two letters followed by 1-4 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10725">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10725">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10726">две буквы (без учета регистра), за которыми следуют 1-4 номера</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10726">two letters (not case sensitive) followed by 1-4 numbers</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10727">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10727">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10728">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10728">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10729">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10729">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10730">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10730">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10731">регулярное выражение Regex_uk_electoral находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10731">The regular expression Regex_uk_electoral finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10732">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_electoral.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10732">A keyword from Keyword_uk_electoral is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.K. Electoral Number -->
<Entity id="a3eea206-dc0c-4f06-9e22-aa1be3059963" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_uk_electoral" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_electoral" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10733">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10733">Keywords</span></span>

## <a name="uk-national-health-service-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10739">Королевств</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10739">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10740">Национальный номер службы работоспособности</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10740">national health service number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10741">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10741">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10742">10–17 цифр, разделенных пробелами.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10742">10-17 digits separated by spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10743">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10743">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10744">10-17 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10744">10-17 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10745">либо три, либо десять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10745">either three or ten digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10746">пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10746">a space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10747">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10747">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10748">пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10748">a space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10749">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10749">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10750">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10750">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10751">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10751">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10752">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10752">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10753">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10753">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10754">Функция Func_uk_nhs_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10754">The function Func_uk_nhs_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10755">Верно одно из условий ниже:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10755">One of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10756">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_nhs_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10756">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nhs_number is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10757">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_nhs_number1;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10757">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nhs_number1 is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10758">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10758">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10759">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10759">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.K. NHS Number -->
<Entity id="3192014e-2a16-44e9-aa69-4b20375c9a78" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_nhs_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nhs_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nhs_number1" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10760">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10760">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_uk_nhs_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10761">Keyword_uk_nhs_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10761">Keyword_uk_nhs_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10762">national health service</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10762">national health service</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10764">health services authority</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10764">health services authority</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10765">health authority</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10765">health authority</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_uk_nhs_number1"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10766">Keyword_uk_nhs_number1</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10766">Keyword_uk_nhs_number1</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10767">patient id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10767">patient id</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10768">patient identification</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10768">patient identification</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10769">patient no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10769">patient no</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10770">patient number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10770">patient number</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10771">Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10771">Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10772">ГРУПП</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10772">GP</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10773">доб</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10773">DOB</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10774">D. O. B</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10774">D.O.B</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10775">Date of Birth</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10775">Date of Birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10776">Birth Date</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10776">Birth Date</span></span> 
   
## <a name="uk-national-insurance-number-nino"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10777">Королевств</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10777">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10778">Национальный страховой номер (Нино)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10778">national insurance number (NINO)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10779">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включен в тип конфиденциальной конфиденциальной информации ЕС Идентификаитон и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10779">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU National Identificaiton Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10780">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10780">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10781">семь символов или девять символов, разделенных пробелами или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10781">seven characters or nine characters separated by spaces or dashes</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10782">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10782">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10783">два возможных шаблона:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10783">two possible patterns:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10784">две буквы (допустимые Нинос используют только определенные символы в этом префиксе, которые пропускаются при проверке этого шаблона; без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10784">two letters (valid NINOs use only certain characters in this prefix, which this pattern validates; not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10785">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10785">six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10786">"A", "B", "C", или "'D" (например, префикс, в суффиксе допускаются только определенные символы; без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10786">either 'A', 'B', 'C', or 'D' (like the prefix, only certain characters are allowed in the suffix; not case sensitive)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10787">OR</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10787">OR</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10788">две буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10788">two letters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10789">пробел или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10789">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10790">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10790">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10791">пробел или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10791">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10792">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10792">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10793">пробел или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10793">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10794">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10794">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10795">пробел или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10795">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10796">значение "A", "B", "C" или "'D"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10796">either 'A', 'B', 'C', or 'D'</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10797">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10797">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10798">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10798">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10799">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10799">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10800">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10800">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10801">функция Func_uk_nino находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10801">The function Func_uk_nino finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10802">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_nino.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10802">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nino is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10803">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10803">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10804">функция Func_uk_nino находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10804">The function Func_uk_nino finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- U.K. NINO -->
    <Entity id="16c07343-c26f-49d2-a987-3daf717e94cc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75" relaxProximity="true">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_nino" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nino" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_nino" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="uk-unique-taxpayer-reference-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10826">Королевств</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10826">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10827">Уникальный номер ссылки налогоплательщика</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10827">Unique Taxpayer Reference Number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10828">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10828">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10829">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10829">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10830">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10830">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10831">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10831">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10832">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10832">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10833">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10833">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10834">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10834">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10835">10 цифр без пробелов и разделителей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10835">10 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
 
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10836">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10836">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10837">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10837">10 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10838">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10838">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10839">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10839">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10840">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10840">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10841">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10841">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10842">Функция  `Func_uk_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10842">The function  `Func_uk_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10843">Найдено ключевое слово FROM  `Keywords_uk_eu_tax_file_number` .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10843">A keyword from  `Keywords_uk_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- U.K. Unique Taxpayer Reference Number -->
      <Entity id="ad4a8116-0db8-439a-b545-6d967642f0ec" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_uk_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="us-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10863">Номер банковского счета США</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10863">U.S. bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10864">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10864">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10865">6-17 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10865">6-17 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10866">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10866">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10867">6-17 последовательных цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10867">6-17 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10868">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10868">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10869">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10869">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10870">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10870">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10871">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10871">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10872">регулярное выражение Regex_usa_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10872">The regular expression Regex_usa_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10873">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_usa_Bank_Account.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10873">A keyword from Keyword_usa_Bank_Account is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.S. Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="a2ce32a8-f935-4bb6-8e96-2a5157672e2c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_usa_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_usa_Bank_Account" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="us-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10903">Номер водительского удостоверения для драйвера США</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10903">U.S. driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10904">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10904">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10905">Зависит от штата.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10905">Depends on the state</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10906">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10906">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10907">зависит от штата — например, Нью Йорк:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10907">depends on the state -- for example, New York:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10908">девять цифр, отформатированных как DDD DDD DDD, будут совпадают.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10908">nine digits formatted like ddd ddd ddd will match.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10909">девять цифр, такие как ццццццццц, не совпадают.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10909">nine digits like ddddddddd will not match.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10910">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10910">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10911">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10911">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-10912">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10912">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10913">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10913">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10914">функция Func_new_york_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10914">The function Func_new_york_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10915">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10915">A keyword from Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10916">обнаружено ключевое слово из списка Keyword_us_drivers_license.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10916">A keyword from Keyword_us_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-10917">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10917">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10918">функция Func_new_york_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10918">The function Func_new_york_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10919">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10919">A keyword from Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10920">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_us_drivers_license_abbreviations.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10920">A keyword from Keyword_us_drivers_license_abbreviations is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-10921">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_us_drivers_license не находится.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-10921">No keyword from Keyword_us_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

```xml
<Entity id="dfeb356f-61cd-459e-bf0f-7c6d28b458c6 patternsProximity="300">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_york_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_new_york_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_us_drivers_license" />
    </Pattern>
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_york_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_new_york_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_us_drivers_license_abbreviations" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_us_drivers_license" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="us-individual-taxpayer-identification-number-itin"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-11019">Индивидуальный идентификационный номер налогоплательщика (SHAREPOINTВ) для США</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11019">U.S. individual taxpayer identification number (ITIN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-11020">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11020">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-11021">девять цифр, начинающиеся с цифры "9" и содержащие "7" или "8" в качестве четвертой цифры, при необходимости отформатированные с помощью пробелов или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11021">nine digits that start with a "9" and contain a "7" or "8" as the fourth digit, optionally formatted with spaces or dashes</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-11022">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11022">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-11023">форматируемые</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11023">formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-11024">цифра "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11024">the digit "9"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-11025">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11025">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-11026">пробел или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11026">a space or dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-11027">"7" или "8"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11027">a "7" or "8"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-11028">цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11028">a digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-11029">пробел или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11029">a space, or dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-11030">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11030">four digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-11031">неформатированные</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11031">unformatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-11032">цифра "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11032">the digit "9"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-11033">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11033">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-11034">"7" или "8"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11034">a "7" or "8"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-11035">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11035">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-11036">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11036">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-11037">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11037">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-11038">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11038">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-11039">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11039">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-11040">Функция Func_formatted_itin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11040">The function Func_formatted_itin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-11041">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_itin;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11041">A keyword from Keyword_itin is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-11042">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11042">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-11043">Функция Func_unformatted_itin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11043">The function Func_unformatted_itin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-11044">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_itin;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11044">A keyword from Keyword_itin is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-11045">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11045">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-11046">Функция Func_formatted_itin или Func_unformatted_itin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11046">The function Func_formatted_itin or Func_unformatted_itin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- U.S. Individual Taxpayer Identification Number (ITIN) -->
    <Entity id="e55e2a32-f92d-4985-a35d-a0b269eb687b" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_formatted_itin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_itin" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_itin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_itin" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_formatted_itin" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_itin" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-11053">и.т.и.н.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11053">i.t.i.n.</span></span>

## <a name="us-social-security-number-ssn"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-11061">Номер социального страхования (SSN) США</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11061">U.S. social security number (SSN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-11062">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11062">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-11063">девять цифр, которые могут быть в форматированном или неформатированном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11063">nine digits, which may be in a formatted or unformatted pattern</span></span>

> [!NOTE]
> <span data-ttu-id="548bb-11064">Есть SSN выдан до середины 2011 г., он отличается строгим форматированием, при котором определенные части номера должны входить в указанные диапазоны (при этом нет контрольной суммы).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11064">If issued before mid-2011, an SSN has strong formatting where certain parts of the number must fall within certain ranges to be valid (but there's no checksum).</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-11065">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11065">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-11066">четыре функции ищут служб SSNs в четырех различных шаблонах:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11066">four functions look for SSNs in four different patterns:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-11067">Func_ssn находит SSN со строгим форматированием с тире или пробелами, выданные до 2011 г. (ццц-цц-цццц ИЛИ ццц цц цццц);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11067">Func_ssn finds SSNs with pre-2011 strong formatting that are formatted with dashes or spaces (ddd-dd-dddd OR ddd dd dddd)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-11068">Func_unformatted_ssn находит SSN со строгим форматированием, выданные до 2011 г. (без форматирования в виде девяти последовательных цифр — ццццццццц);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11068">Func_unformatted_ssn finds SSNs with pre-2011 strong formatting that are unformatted as nine consecutive digits (ddddddddd)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-11069">Func_randomized_formatted_ssn находит SSN с тире или пробелами, выданные после 2011 г. (ццц-цц-цццц ИЛИ ццц цц цццц);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11069">Func_randomized_formatted_ssn finds post-2011 SSNs that are formatted with dashes or spaces (ddd-dd-dddd OR ddd dd dddd)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-11070">Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn находит SSN без форматирования в виде девяти последовательных цифр, выданные после 2011 г. (ццццццццц).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11070">Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn finds post-2011 SSNs that are unformatted as nine consecutive digits (ddddddddd)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-11071">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11071">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-11072">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11072">No</span></span>


### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-11073">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11073">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-11074">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11074">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-11075">Функция Func_ssn находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11075">The function Func_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-11076">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_ssn.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11076">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-11077">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11077">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-11078">Функция Func_unformatted_ssn находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11078">The function Func_unformatted_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-11079">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_ssn.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11079">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-11080">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11080">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-11081">Функция Func_randomized_formatted_ssn находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11081">The function Func_randomized_formatted_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-11082">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_ssn.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11082">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-11083">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 55 % верно обнаружила этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в пределах ближайших 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11083">A DLP policy is 55% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-11084">Функция Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11084">The function Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-11085">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_ssn.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11085">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>


```xml
<!-- U.S. Social Security Number (SSN) -->
  <Entity id="a44669fe-0d48-453d-a9b1-2cc83f2cba77" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_randomized_formatted_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="55">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
  </Entity>
```

## <a name="us--uk-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-11100">США/ВЕЛИКОБРИТАНИЯ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11100">U.S. / U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="548bb-11101">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11101">passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-11102">Великобритания</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11102">The U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="548bb-11103">Объект типа конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта доступен в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС и доступен как отдельный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11103">passport number sensitive information type entity is available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-11104">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11104">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-11105">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11105">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-11106">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11106">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-11107">девять последовательных цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11107">nine consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-11108">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11108">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-11109">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11109">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-11110">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11110">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-11111">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11111">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-11112">функция Func_usa_uk_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11112">The function Func_usa_uk_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-11113">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11113">A keyword from Keyword_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<Entity id="178ec42a-18b4-47cc-85c7-d62c92fd67f8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_usa_uk_passport" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_passport" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="ukraine-passport-domestic"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-11134">Украина Passport Россия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11134">Ukraine passport domestic</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-11135">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11135">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-11136">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11136">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-11137">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11137">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-11138">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11138">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-11139">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11139">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-11140">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11140">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-11141">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11141">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-11142">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11142">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-11143">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11143">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-11144">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11144">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-11145">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11145">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-11146">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11146">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-11147">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11147">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-11148">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11148">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-11149">Регулярное выражение Regex_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11149">The regex Regex_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-11150">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11150">A keyword from Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Ukraine Passport Domestic -->
      <Entity id="1817a540-221f-4459-9202-3bd78b81d803" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic"/>
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic"/>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="ukraine-passport-international"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-11159">Украина Passport International</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11159">Ukraine passport international</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="548bb-11160">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации можно использовать только в следующих целях:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11160">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-11161">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11161">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-11162">политики соответствия требованиям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11162">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-11163">Управление сведениями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11163">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-11164">Управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11164">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-11165">Microsoft Cloud App Security</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11165">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-11166">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11166">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-11167">буквенно-цифровой шаблон из восьми символов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11167">eight-character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-11168">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11168">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-11169">8-значный буквенно-цифровой шаблон:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11169">eight-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-11170">две буквы или цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11170">two letters or digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-11171">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11171">six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-11172">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11172">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-11173">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11173">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="548bb-11174">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11174">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="548bb-11175">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11175">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-11176">Регулярное выражение Regex_Ukraine_Passport_International находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11176">The regex Regex_Ukraine_Passport_International finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="548bb-11177">Найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_International.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="548bb-11177">A keyword from Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_International is found.</span></span>
